d%20for%20the%20Republican%20billionaire%2C%20Fulton%20County%20Superior%20Court%20Judge%20Scott%20McAfee%20imposed%20several%20conditions%20in%20an%20agreement%20approved%20by%20prosecutors%20and%20Trump%20attorneys.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Defendant%20shall%20perform%20no%20act%20to%20intimidate%20any%20person%20known%20to%20him%20or%20her%20to%20be%20a%20codefendant%20or%20witness%20in%20this%20case%20or%20to%20otherwise%20obstruct%20the%20administration%20of%20justice%2C%26quot%3B%20McAfee%20said%20in%20a%20three-page%20court%20filing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20above%20shall%20include%2C%20but%20are%20not%20limited%20to%2C%20posts%20on%20social%20media%20or%20reposts%20of%20posts%20made%20by%20another%20individual%20on%20social%20media%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMcAfee%20set%20bond%20at%20%24100%2C000%20each%20for%20two%20co-defendants%20in%20the%20case%20--%20former%20Trump%20campaign%20attorneys%20John%20Eastman%20and%20Kenneth%20Chesebro.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWillis%2C%20the%20Fulton%20County%20district%20attorney%2C%20has%20asked%20the%20judge%20to%20set%20a%20trial%20date%20of%20March%204%20next%20year%20for%20the%2077-year-old%20former%20president%20on%20charges%20of%20trying%20to%20overturn%20the%202020%20presidential%20election%20result%20in%20Georgia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20is%20facing%20four%20criminal%20trials%20as%20he%20bids%20for%20a%20return%20to%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20was%20indicted%20in%20Georgia%20on%20charges%20of%20racketeering%20and%20a%20string%20of%20election%20crimes%20after%20a%20sprawling%2C%20two-year%20probe%20into%20his%20efforts%20to%20overturn%20his%20election%20defeat%20to%20Biden%20in%20the%20Peach%20State.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOthers%20facing%20charges%20in%20the%20alleged%20conspiracy%20include%20Trump's%20former%20personal%20lawyer%20Rudy%20Giuliani%20and%20his%20White%20House%20chief%20of%20staff%2C%20Mark%20Meadows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20'Speedy%20trial'%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpecial%20counsel%20Jack%20Smith%20has%20asked%20a%20federal%20judge%20to%20set%20a%20January%202%2C%202024%20date%20for%20the%20former%20president%20to%20go%20on%20trial%20in%20Washington%20on%20separate%20charges%20of%20conspiring%20to%20upend%20the%20results%20of%20the%202020%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20attorneys%20asked%20Judge%20Tanya%20Chutkan%20last%20week%20to%20schedule%20the%20trial%20for%20April%202026%20--%20long%20after%20next%20year's%20presidential%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20argued%20that%20the%20amount%20of%20documents%20in%20the%20case%20would%20require%20months%20to%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESmith%20pushed%20back%20in%20a%20court%20filing%20on%20Monday%20saying%20Trump's%20defense%20team%20%26quot%3Bexaggerates%20the%20challenge%20of%20reviewing%26quot%3B%20the%20evidence%20presented%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20proposed%20trial%20date%20in%202026%20would%20deny%20the%20public%20its%20right%20to%20a%20speedy%20trial%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20special%20counsel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChutkan%20is%20to%20decide%20the%20date%20for%20the%20trial%20at%20a%20hearing%20on%20August%2028.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20also%20faces%20a%20trial%20in%20New%20York%20in%20March%202024%20for%20allegedly%20making%20hush%20money%20payments%20to%20a%20porn%20star%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20cheat%20campaign%20finance%20rules%20ahead%20of%20the%202016%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20scheduled%20to%20go%20on%20trial%20in%20Florida%20in%20May%20on%20charges%20also%20brought%20by%20Smith%20of%20mishandling%20top%20secret%20government%20documents%20he%20took%20from%20the%20White%20House%20as%20he%20left%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692664980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.co