target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehitting%20some%20snags%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20its%20inaugural%20NFL%20%26quot%3BThursday%20Night%20Football%26quot%3B%20season%20on%20Prime%20Video%20last%20year%2C%20Amazon%20is%20bringing%20plenty%20of%20swagger%20to%20the%20field%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20is%20getting%20more%20TV%20ad%20dollars%20this%20year%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-sag-aftra-actors-wga-writers-unions-strike-hollywood%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etwin%20Hollywood%20strikes%3C%2Fa%3E%20rage%20on%2C%20a%20top%20exec%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20of%20the%20strikes%2C%20more%20ad%20dollars%20are%20flowing%20to%20live%20sports%2C%20and%20there's%20nothing%20more%20exciting%20than%20live%20sports%2C%26quot%3B%20Jay%20Marine%2C%20Amazon's%20VP%20of%20Prime%20Video%20and%20global%20head%20of%20sports%2C%20said%20during%20a%20Zoom%20press%20conference%20Monday%20previewing%20the%20fall%20season.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20getting%20more%20than%20our%20share.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarine%20and%20%26quot%3BTNF%26quot%3B%20talent%20like%20Al%20Michaels%20and%20Kaylee%20Hartung%20also%20talked%20up%20the%20fall%20schedule%20that'll%20include%20key%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D70f494366ed9aa273ca2e5cb95784086fd47b8f701ebb0b43d1f6e114fff554b%26postID%3D64e3be37f87b369c6da4665e%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.aboutamazon.com%252Fnews%252Fentertainment%252Fthursday-night-football-schedule-2023%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ematchups%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20NFL's%20first%20Black%20Friday%20game%2C%20which%20will%20air%20free%20to%20all%20fans%3B%20and%20new%20audience%20targeting%20capabilities%20and%20interactive%20ads.%20The%2016-game%20season%20kicks%20off%20September%2014%20with%20the%20Minnesota%20Vikings%20facing%20the%20Philadelphia%20Eagles%3B%20a%20preseason%20game%20will%20stream%20August%2024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20additional%20creative%20function%20is%20a%20big%20deal%2C%26quot%3B%20Marine%20said%20of%20Amazon's%20ad%20offerings.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20Toyota%2C%20now%20you%20can%20buy%20one%20slot%20and%20have%20a%20creative%20targeted%20to%20a%20family%20for%20mini%20vans%2C%20and%20you%20can%20have%20a%20different%20creative%20in%20that%20same%20slot%20buy%20for%20a%20truck%20commercial%20to%20different%20fans.%20Historically%2C%20you%20haven't%20been%20able%20to%20do%20that%20on%20traditional%20broadcast.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAd%20buyers%20confirmed%20to%20Insider%20that%20Amazon%20was%20benefitting%20from%20advertisers'%20moving%20as%20much%20as%2020%25%20of%20their%20primetime%20TV%20budgets%20out%20of%20network%20TV%20and%20cable%20because%20of%20the%20strikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20has%20also%20come%20way%20down%20in%20ad%20prices%20and%20is%20matching%20other%20NFL%20broadcasters%20like%20Fox%20and%20ESPN%20in%20rates%2C%20one%20ad%20exec%20told%20Insider.%20It's%20a%20big%20shift%20from%20last%20year%20when%20Amazon%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-thursday-night-football-nielsen-audience-cuts-advertising-prices-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Einitially%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20sought%20to%20charge%20%2480%20to%20reach%20one%20thousand%20viewers%2C%20or%20double%20the%20broadcast%20rates.%20Amazon%20last%20year%20had%20also%20softened%20on%20its%20initial%20ask%20that%20advertisers%20buy%20the%20entire%20season's%20games%20and%20gave%20them%20the%20option%20to%20buy%20a%20portion%20of%20the%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarine%20left%20no%20question%20as%20to%20whether%20Amazon%20would%20continue%20to%20be%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-sports-could-fuel-amazons-advertising-ambitions-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebig%20player%20in%20live%20sports%3C%2Fa%3E.%20At%20a%20time%20when%20sports%20rights%20fees%20are%20soaring%2C%20putting%20a%20financial%20strain%20on%