0Nystr%C3%B6m%2FF%C3%B6rsvarsmakten%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ENATO%20and%20European%20countries%20have%20started%20training%20Ukrainians%20on%20advanced%20F-16%20fighter%20jets.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EInsider%20obtained%20a%20copy%20of%20a%20document%20outlining%20the%20training%20program%20and%20how%20it%20will%20unfold.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20document%20suggests%20that%20other%20jets%20could%20be%20added%20at%20some%20point%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20pilots%20and%20personnel%20have%20already%20started%20training%20on%20F-16s%2C%20Kyiv%20has%20said%2C%20and%20a%20plan%20by%20NATO%20members%20and%20partners%20for%20the%20program%20suggests%20Kyiv%20could%20eventually%20learn%20to%20operate%20other%20fighter%20aircraft%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20coalition%20of%2011%20countries%20%E2%80%94%20led%20by%20NATO%20allies%20Denmark%20and%20the%20Netherlands%20%E2%80%94%20has%20committed%20to%20training%20the%20Ukrainians%20on%20how%20to%20operate%20and%20maintain%20the%20F-16s.%20The%20US%20last%20week%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-f16s-wont-start-defeating-russia-air-defenses-2023-8%5C%22%3Efinally%20approved%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20delivery%20of%20the%20American-made%20aircraft%20from%20Copenhagen%20and%20Amsterdam%20to%20Kyiv%2C%20allowing%20the%20training%20program%20to%20move%20forward%20and%20clearing%20the%20way%20for%20F-16s%20to%20be%20sent%20to%20Ukraine%2C%C2%A0possibly%20by%20early%20next%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20months-long%20program%20intends%20to%20cover%20language%20training%2C%20flight%20training%2C%20and%20conversion%20to%20the%20F-16%20platform%2C%C2%A0%20according%20to%20an%20undated%20copy%20of%20the%20F-16%20training%20concept%20that%20Insider%20obtained%20from%20the%20Danish%20defense%20ministry.%20The%20document%20also%20hints%20that%20Ukraine%20might%20get%20its%20hands%20on%20other%20fighter%20jets%20at%20some%20point.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlong%20various%20training%20tracks%2C%20which%20will%20be%20carried%20out%20in%20concert%20by%20the%20members%20of%20the%20coalition%2C%20Ukrainian%20fighter%20pilots%20and%20support%20personnel%20will%20be%20trained%20to%20operate%2C%20support%20and%20maintain%20the%20F-16%20fighter%20aircraft%20at%20a%20basic%20tactical%20and%20technical%20level%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20document%20reads%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere%20will%20be%20a%20possibility%20to%20include%20other%20types%20of%20fighter%20aircrafts%20at%20a%20later%20stage.%26quot%3B%20A%20separate%20statement%20said%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20immediately%20clear%20which%20fighter%20aircraft%20the%20statement%20is%20referencing%2C%20but%20one%20aircraft%20that%20the%20Ukrainians%20have%20been%20eyeing%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-asking-for-f16s-but-also-looking-at-swedish-gripens-2023-7%5C%22%3ESweden's%20JAS%2039%20Gripen%3C%2Fa%3E.%20These%20jets%20are%20considered%20by%20experts%20to%20be%20highly%20capable%20and%20can%20be%20outfitted%20with%20advanced%20air-to-air%20missiles%20and%20intimidating%20air-to-surface%20missiles%20and%20bombs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Saab%20JAS-39C%20Gripen%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64bac4bd006a5e00194a3b94%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221332%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Saab%20JAS-39C%20Gripen%20at%20RAF%20Fairford%20during%20the%20Royal%20Military%20Air%20Tattoo%20on%20July%2015%2C%202023.%3Cp%3EMatthew%20Horwood%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Gripen%20could%20prove%20beneficial%20to%20the%20Ukrainians%20because%20the%20aircraft's%20electronic-warfare%20capabilities%20were%20designed%20to%20counter%20Russian%20air-defense%20systems%2C%20it%20is%20relatively%20inexpensive%20to%20operate%2C%20and%20it%20requires%20less%20runway%20space%20for%20taking%20off%20and%20landing.%20However%2C%20the%20jet%20is%20operated%20by%20just%20six%20countries%20%E2%80%94%20only%20two%20of%20which%20support%20Ukraine%20with%20military%20aid%20(Sweden%20and%20the%20Czech%20Republic)%20%E2%80%94%20and%20has%20not%20yet%20seen%20combat%20experience.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESweden%2C%20an%20aspiring%20NATO%20member%20and%20longstanding%20partner%20of%20the%20military%20alliance%2C%20has%20repeatedly%20ruled%20out%20sending%20its%20Gripens%20to%20Kyiv%2C%20asserting%20that%20it%20needs%20the%20fighter%20jets%20for%20its%20own%20national%20security%20interests.%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%20said%20on%20Sunday%20that%20Kyiv%20had%20achieved%20a%20%26quot%3Bbreakthrough%20result%26quot%3B%20regarding%20Gripens%20after%20spending%20the%20day%20in%20Sweden%2C%20although%20Stockholm%20appeared%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FKyivIndependent%2Fstatus%2F1693642207855550781%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Epour%20cold%20water%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20his%20excitement%20the%20next%20day%20by%20stating%20that%20there%20are%20no%20plans%20to%20transfer%20the%20jets%20to%20Ukraine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20soldiers%20are%20already%20starting%20to%20test%20them.%20And%20we%20are%20step%20by%20step%2C%20negotiation%20by%20negotiation%2C%20we%20are%20getting%20closer%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20Gripen%20fighters%20will%20appear%20in%20our%20sky%2C%26quot%3B%20Zelenskyy%20said%20during%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.president.gov.ua%2Fen%2Fnews%2Fkrok-za-krokom-nablizhayemosya-do-togo-shob-shvedski-litaki-84981%5C%22%3Eaddress%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20nation.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20working%20on%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20stage%20with%20the%20training%20of%20our%20boys%20on%20Gripen%20fighters.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESweden%20is%20part%20of%20the%2011-country%20coalition%20training%20Ukrainians%20on%20F-16s%2C%20which%20includes%20Belgium%2C%20Canada%2C%20Denmark%2C%20Luxembourg%2C%20the%20Netherlands%2C%20Norway%2C%20Poland%2C%20Portugal%2C%20Romania%20and%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20which%20have%20an%20assortment%20of%20fighter%20aircraft%20available.%20According%20to%20the%20Danish%20defense%20ministry%20document%2C%20participants%20in%20the%20four-phase%20training%20initiative%20will%20include%20Ukrainian%20technicians%2C%20support%20staff%2C%20mission%20planners%2C%20and%20pilots%20with%20varying%20levels%20of%20experience.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20coalition%20has%20agreed%20to%20support%20the%20training%20with%20language%20experts%2C%20pilots%2C%20ground%20crew%2C%20instructors%2C%20aircraft%20or%20funding%20as%20appropriate%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20document%20reads.%20%26quot%3BUkraine%20is%20expected%20to%20provide%20qualified%20personnel%20able%20to%20pass%20necessary%20language%2C%20health%20and%20security%20tests.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Czech%20Republic%20JAS-39%20Gripen%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F638678c265ca3a0018ffb760%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221364%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20JAS-39%20Gripen%20at%20a%20military%20base%20near%20Prague%20on%20April%2018%2C%202005.%3Cp%3EREUTERS%2FPetr%20Josek%20PJ%2FAA%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EZelenskyy%20said%20on%20Sunday%20that%20Ukrainian%20personnel%20had%20already%20started%20training%20on%20the%20F-16%20in%20Denmark.%20Kyiv%20won't%20receive%20the%20jets%20until%20the%20training%20program%20is%20complete%2C%20which%20could%20be%20as%20soon%20as%20early%20next%20year%2C%20but%20the%20training%20concept%20document%20says%20that%20the%20timing%20will%20ultimately%20depend%20on%20the%20qualifications%20of%20all%20the%20participants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20the%20training%20will%20take%20place%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20but%20it%20could%20happen%20at%20various%20locations%20in%20Europe%2C%20according%20to%20the%20document.%20A%20Pentagon