20a%20dozen%20people%20dialed%20into%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F23919674-continued-section-341-meeting-of-creditors%23document%2Fp1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econference%20call%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0hosted%20by%20the%20US%20Trustee's%20office%2C%20which%20is%20overseeing%20the%20Corizon%20bankruptcy.%20It%20was%20one%20of%20a%20series%20of%20so-called%20341%20meetings%20%E2%80%94%20a%20chance%20for%20creditors%20owed%20money%20by%20a%20bankrupt%20company%20to%20get%20their%20questions%20answered.%20Representing%20Tehum%2C%20the%20company%20now%20saddled%20with%20Corizon's%20debts%2C%20were%20the%20chief%20restructuring%20officer%20and%20Tehum's%20director%2C%20Isaac%20Lefkowitz%2C%20who%20would%20speak%20under%20oath.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECivil%20rights%20and%20bankruptcy%20attorneys%2C%20lawyers%20for%20a%20committee%20of%20the%20unsecured%20creditors%2C%20including%20the%20University%20of%20Missouri%2C%20and%20two%20Insider%20reporters%20were%20on%20the%20three-hour%20call%2C%20as%20Lefkowitz%20explained%20why%20bankruptcy%20was%20Corizon's%20best%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20entering%20correctional%20healthcare%2C%20Lefkowitz%20dabbled%20over%20the%20decades%20in%20real%20estate%2C%20oncology%2C%20medical%20practice%20management%20%E2%80%94%20even%20the%20sale%20of%20mixed%20nuts.%20In%20many%20business%20endeavors%2C%20records%20show%2C%20he%20has%20been%20sued%3B%20he%20also%20once%20landed%20in%20trouble%20with%20regulators.%20He's%20been%20involved%20in%20at%20least%20six%20bankruptcies%20%E2%80%94%20including%20four%20as%20an%20owner%20or%20manager%20%E2%80%94%20and%20has%20also%20been%20accused%20in%20court%20filings%20of%20fraud%20or%20bad-faith%20conduct%20on%20multiple%20occasions%20that%20have%20resulted%20in%20settlements.%20A%20brief%20filed%20in%20the%20bankruptcy%20case%20describes%20Lefkowitz%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bprolific%20filer%20of%20Chapter%2011%20petitions%26quot%3B%20who%20often%20leverages%20the%20bankruptcy%20process%20to%20%26quot%3Bavoid%20unsatisfactory%20outcomes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20once%20sued%20by%20the%20son%20of%20a%20close%20friend%2C%20who%20claimed%20in%20a%20lawsuit%20that%20Lefkowitz%20swindled%20the%20son's%20late%20father%20out%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20while%20advising%20on%20his%20US%20real-estate%20portfolio.%20The%20son%2C%20Simche%20Steinberger%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%20Lefkowitz%20showed%20off%20his%20wealth%20like%20%26quot%3Bthe%20Queen%20of%20England%26quot%3B%20and%20convinced%20Steinberger's%20dad%20he'd%20be%20lucky%20to%20invest.%20Lefkowitz%20and%20the%20father%20shared%20%26quot%3Bunconditional%20trust%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F23919675-simche-steinberger-complaint%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecomplaint%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20%26quot%3Bthey%20knew%20and%20socialized%20with%20each%20other%20and%20came%20from%20an%20extraordinarily%20insular%20and%20exceptionally%20close-knit%20religious%20community.%26quot%3B%20The%20complaint%20also%20accuses%20Lefkowitz%20of%20fraud%2C%20deceit%2C%20embezzlement%2C%20and%20purloining%20funds.%20%26quot%3BThis%20guy's%20a%20crook%2C%26quot%3B%20Steinberger%20said.%20%26quot%3BHe%20knows%20how%20to%20play%20around%20with%20laws.%26quot%3B%20The%20case%20was%20dismissed%20for%20lack%20of%20standing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20Flacks%2C%20the%20chairman%20and%20CEO%20of%20Flacks%20Group%2C%20which%20sold%20Corizon%20to%20the%20new%20buyers%2C%20confirmed%20that%20Lefkowitz%20has%20enjoyed%20a%20lavish%20lifestyle%2C%20telling%20Insider%20Lefkowitz%20has%20vacationed%20for%20years%20on%20Fisher%20Island%2C%20an%20exclusive%20Florida%20island%20that%20is%20home%20to%20the%20country's%20richest%20ZIP%20code.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELefkowitz%20appears%20to%20have%20had%20no%20previous%20experience%20with%20prisons%20and%20jails%20bef