firm%20where%20he's%20a%20director.%20He%20responded%20from%20a%20YesCare%20email%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BOur%20policy%20is%20not%20to%20comment%20during%20pending%20company%20litigation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20later%20followed%20up%20from%20a%20Perigrove%20email%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20subject%20companies%20in%20your%20proposed%20write-up%20provide%20a%20vital%20service%20to%20the%20incarcerated%20because%20we%20believe%20healthcare%20is%20a%20basic%20human%20right%20that%20should%20be%20afforded%20to%20everyone%2C%20regardless%20of%20past%20mistakes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20adverse%20accusations%20in%20your%20proposed%20piece%20are%20sourced%20from%20allegations%20in%20public%20filings%20that%20are%20riddled%20with%20false%20accusations%20and%20inaccurate%20information%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Corizon%20bankruptcy%20is%20presently%20in%20a%20court%20ordered%20mediation%2C%20and%20we%20are%20seeking%20a%20global%20resolution%20for%20all%20the%20parties%20involved.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F23919677-the-official-committee-of-unsecured-creditors-motion-to-compel-geneva-consulting-llcs-compliance-with-subpoena%23document%2Fp34%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELefkowitz%20deposition%3C%2Fa%3E%20filed%20in%20court%20in%20June%20revealed%20that%20he%20had%20a%205%25%20stake%20in%20Perigrove%201018.%20He%20also%20finally%20named%20two%20others%20in%20the%20group%20of%20investors%3A%20David%20Gefner%20and%20Abraham%20Goldberger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELawsuits%20that%20claim%20fraud%2C%20embezzlement%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20Lefkowitz%2C%20Gefner%20and%20Goldberger%20are%20associated%20with%20multiple%20business%20that%20have%20filed%20for%20bankruptcy%20or%20faced%20allegations%20of%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGefner%2C%20who%20turns%2030%20this%20month%2C%20says%20on%20LinkedIn%20he%20founded%20Perigrove%2C%20the%20private%20equity%20firm%2C%20in%202012%2C%20while%20he%20was%20still%20a%20teenager.%20Since%20then%2C%20documents%20show%2C%20he%20has%20spun%20out%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20Perigrove%20entities%2C%20registered%20in%20his%20name%20at%20the%20same%20address%20in%20Suffern%2C%20a%20New%20York%20suburb%20in%20Rockland%20County.%20Among%20them%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F23919678-perigrove-1018-llc-articles-of-organization%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPerigrove%201018%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerigrove%20was%20a%20central%20player%20in%20the%20purchase%20of%20Corizon%20from%20Flacks%20Group%2C%20according%20to%20Flacks%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F23919686-james-hyman-complaint%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elawsuit%3C%2Fa%3E%20filed%20by%20Hyman%2C%20Corizon's%20former%20CEO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGefner's%20LinkedIn%20profile%20describes%20him%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bvisionary%20entrepreneur%26quot%3B%20who%20has%20closed%20several%20merger-and-acquisition%20transactions%20across%20real%20estate%20and%20healthcare.%20It%20says%20that%20in%202009%2C%20when%20he%20would%20have%20been%20in%20high%20school%2C%20he%20served%20as%20an%20acquisitions%20specialist%20%26quot%3Bfor%20an%20exclusive%20network%20of%20family%20offices%20and%20ultra-high%20net%20worth%20investors.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGefner%20also%20says%20on%20LinkedIn%20that%20he's%20a%20board%20member%20at%20Consulate%20Health%20Care%2C%20once%20the%20country's%20sixth-largest%20nursing-home%20chain.%20Consulate%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tampabay.com%2Fnews%2Fhealth%2F2022%2F01%2F19%2Fconsulate-nursing-homes-are-changing-names-are-they-changing-ownership%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egained%20notoriety%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20a%20federal%20civil%20jury%20found%20in%202017%20that%20the%20company%20had%20defrauded%20taxpayers%20with%20inflated%20billings%20for%20resident%20care.%20That%20case%20was%20nearing%20a%20settlement%20in%20March%202021%20when%20Consulate%2C%20in%20a%20surprise%20move%2C%20filed%20for%20bankruptcy.%20The%20Justice%20Department%20ultimately%20agreed%20to%20settle%20the%20%24256%20million%20civil%20fraud%20judgment%20for%20just%20%244.5%20million.%20Consulate's%20CEO%20and%20Gefner's%20attorney%2C%20Terrence%20A.%20Oved%2C%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20queries%20seeking%20confirmation%20of%20Gefner's%20claim.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20recently%20as%20March%20of%20this%20year%2C%20a%20pair%20of%20companies%20Gefner%20set%20up%20faced%20a%20fraud%20lawsuit%20over%20claims%20they'd%20failed%20to%20repay%20millions%20of%20dollars%20in%20loans%20intended%20to%20develop%20a%20boutique%20Brooklyn%20hotel%3B%20Gefner%20personally%20settled%20before%20the%20suit%20was%20filed%2C%20according%20to%20the%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOved%20responded%20to%20queries%20on%20Gefner's%20behalf%20with%20a%20statement%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BDavid%20Gefner%20has%20never%20personally%20filed%20for%20bankruptcy%20or%20been%20involved%20in%20a%20litigation%20where%20he%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20fraud%3B%20nor%20does%20he%20control%20any%20company%20that%20has%20filed%20for%20bankruptcy.%20The%20attempt%20to%20tarnish%20his%20reputation%20by%20association%20and%20implication%20is%20regrettable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGefner%20has%20been%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20Corizon%20Two-Step.%20He%20was%20for%20a%20time%20listed%20as%20a%20director%20for%20Tehum.%20And%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F23919679-yescare-holdings-llc-articles-of-organization%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincorporation%20records%3C%2Fa%3E%20show%20he's%20the%20organizer%20for%20YesCare%20Holdings%20LLC%20%E2%80%94%20the%20holding%20company%20with%20a%2095%25%20ownership%20stake%20in%20YesCare%20Corp.%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20owns%20YesCare%2C%20the%20company%20with%20Corizon's%20active%20contracts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20also%20listed%20in%20a%20December%202022%20business%20filing%20as%20YesCare%20Corp.'s%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22raw%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2Fe9vCU%2F10%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Key%20players%20have%20straddled%20both%20of%20sides%20of%20the%20Two-Step%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22474%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20investor%20Lefkowitz%20named%2C%20Goldberger%2C%20has%20an%20equally%20tumultuous%20business%20background%20%E2%80%94%20and%20his%20name%20is%20also%20associated%20with%20a%20range%20of%20Corizon-related%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldberger%2C%20who%2C%20like%20Lefkowitz%20and%20Gefner%2C%20has%20a%20Perigrove%20email%20address%2C%20was%20once%20listed%20in%20business%20filings%20as%20a%20director%20and%20officer%20of%20Corizon%20and%20as%20a%20director%20of%20Tehum.%20He's%20listed%20too%20as%20the%20authorized%20person%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F23919680-m2-holdco-reinstatement%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EM2%20HoldCo%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F23919681-m2-loanco-reinstatement%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EM2%20LoanCo%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20company%20that%20gave%20Tehum%20%2439%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldberger%20has%20a%20history%20of%20suing%20his%20business%20partners%20%E2%80%94%20and%20being%20sued%20by%20contractors%20over%20failure%20to%20pay.%20In%202013%20he%20was%20accused%20in%20court%20of%20embezzling%20funds%20from%20a%20charter-jet%20company%2C%20a%20case%20that%20was%20settled%20for%20an%20undisclosed%20sum.%20He's%20now%2