dividuals%20including%20Goldberger%2C%20who%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bwas%20deeply%20involved%20in%20driving%20the%20transaction%20to%20a%20successful%20conclusion.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFlacks%20called%20Goldberger%20%26quot%3BMr.%20Moneyman.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20named%20Joel%20Landau%2C%20someone%20with%20a%20background%20in%20skilled%20nursing%20facilities%2C%20as%20a%20minority%20investor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldberger's%20attorney%2C%20Joseph%20Haspel%2C%20responded%20to%20queries%20with%20a%20statement%20saying%20that%20%26quot%3BMr.%20Goldberger%20is%20a%20passive%20investor%26quot%3B%20in%20Corizon%2C%20Tehum%2C%20YesCare%2C%20Perigrove%2C%20and%20Perigrove%201018.%20%26quot%3BHe%20takes%20the%20position%20that%20it%20is%20for%20the%20Courts%20to%20address%20legal%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20Haspel%20said.%20%26quot%3BHe%20has%20not%20engaged%20in%20any%20wrongdoing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Landau's%20attorney%2C%20Andrew%20Levander%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20any%20%26quot%3Bsuggestion%20that%20Mr.%20Landau%20has%20ever%20had%20an%20ownership%20interest%20or%20investment%20in%20YesCare%2C%20Tehum%20or%20M2%20is%20false.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr.%20Landau%20has%20no%20direct%20or%20indirect%20ownership%20interest%20in%20any%20of%20those%20entities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20buyers%20conducted%20a%20couple%20of%20weeks%20of%20diligence%2C%20Flacks%20said.%20A%20Corizon%20source%20who%20was%20present%20on%20early%20calls%20to%20discuss%20the%20sale%20in%20December%202021%20said%20the%20talks%20moved%20quickly.%20Lefkowitz%20and%20Goldberger%20were%20initially%20interested%20in%20exploring%20a%20purchase%20of%20Corizon's%20pharmacy-management%20subsidiary%2C%20Pharmacorr%2C%20the%20source%20said.%20Within%20the%20week%2C%20they%20had%20decided%20to%20buy%20the%20entire%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20able%20to%20successfully%20negotiate%20a%20corporate%20downsizing%20as%20well%20as%20the