-fight-russia-fpv-drones-report-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecredits%20his%20video%20game%20obsession%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20his%20ability%20to%20effectively%20strike%20Russian%20targets%20using%20drones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20soldier%20told%20The%20Guardian%20in%20an%20interview%20that%20an%20exercise%2C%20which%20involved%20the%20use%20of%20a%20VR%20headset%20and%20a%20joystick%2C%20was%20%26quot%3Blike%20playing%20a%20computer%20game.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20it's%20not%20unheard%20of%20for%20games%2C%20some%20of%20which%20are%20more%20simulation-oriented%2C%20to%20be%20used%20as%20training%20tools%20for%20militaries.%20Early%20on%20in%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20when%20soldiers%20couldn't%20pile%20into%20a%20tank%20or%20simulator%20together%2C%20some%20US%20Army%20tank%20crews%20used%20the%20free%20online%20multiplayer%20game%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcoronavirus-us-army-tank-crews-play-video-games-to-train-2020-4%5C%22%3EWar%20Thunder%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20training%20purposes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20World%20of%20Tanks%2C%20%26quot%3Byou%20are%20kind%20of%20learning%20to%20work%20in%20a%20team%20and%20developing%20tactics%20in%20the%20game%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Ukrainian%20soldier%20told%20The%20Times.%20He%20added%20that%20he%20is%20often%20%26quot%3Btrying%20to%20use%20the%20same%20maneuvers%20as%20in%20real%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20many%20tank%20operators%C2%A0and%20other%20troops%20fighting%20on%20the%20front%20lines%2C%20playing%20World%20of%20Tanks%20is%20less%20about%20learning%20real-world%20skills%20and%20more%20about%20taking%20a%20break%20from%20operating%20tanks%20and%20other%20weapons%20in%20real%20life%20by%20operating%20them%20virtually.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20news%20came%20as%20a%20shock%20to%20soldiers%20in%20a%20Ukrainian%20drone%20unit%2C%20however%2C%20with%20one%20soldier%20asking%20The%20Times%2C%20%26quot%3BWhy%20would%20we%20play%20World%20of%20Tanks%20when%20it's%