s%20women%20and%20child%20development%20department%20--%20allegedly%20raped%20the%20girl%20several%20times%20between%20November%202020%20and%20January%202021%2C%20a%20senior%20police%20officer%20had%20said.%20His%20wife%20allegedly%20gave%20the%20girl%20medicine%20to%20terminate%20her%20pregnancy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhakha%20and%20his%20wife%20were%20arrested%20after%20questioning%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Commission%20for%20Women%20(DCW)%20chairperson%20alleged%20that%20the%20hospital%20authorities%20did%20not%20allow%20her%20to%20meet%20the%20survivor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20director%20of%20the%20hospital%20came%20to%20meet%20the%20DCW%20chief%20and%20informed%20her%20that%20DCP%20(deputy%20commissioner%20of%20police)%20and%20ACP%20(assistant%20commissioner%20of%20police)%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20are%20inside%20the%20hospital%20and%20had%20asked%20them%20to%20not%20allow%20her%20to%20meet%20the%20victim%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20women's%20panel%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20commission%20also%20sent%20a%20notice%20to%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20and%20the%20city%20government's%20women%20and%20child%20development%20and%20services%20departments%2C%20seeking%20action%20in%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Maliwal%20said%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bshocking%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20Delhi%20police%20did%20not%20arrest%20the%20accused%20even%20eight%20days%20after%20registration%20of%20FIR.%20%26quot%3BEven%20I%20was%20not%20allowed%20to%20meet%20the%20survivor%20on%20behest%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Police.%20I%20will%20meet%20the%20survivor%20and%20provide%20all%20possible%20support%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20women's%20panel%20has%20also%20asked%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20to%20provide%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20FIR%20along%20with%20the%20details%20of%20arrests.%20It%20has%20also%20sought%20the%20details%20of%20action%20taken%20by%20the%20city%20government%20against%20the%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5C