20the%20BRICS%20(Brazil-Russia-India-China-South%20Africa)%20summit%20in%20Johannesburg%20are%20being%20finalised%2C%20Foreign%20Secretary%20Vinay%20Kwatra%20said%20on%20Monday.%20But%20he%20did%20not%20give%20a%20direct%20reply%20on%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20meeting%20between%20PM%20Modi%20and%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi%20is%20leaving%20for%20the%20South%20African%20city%20on%20Tuesday%20on%20a%20three-day%20visit%20to%20attend%20the%20first%20in-person%20summit%20of%20the%20BRICS%20since%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20whether%20PM%20Modi%20and%20President%20Xi%20will%20hold%20talks%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20summit%2C%20Mr%20Kwatra%20said%20that%20the%20schedule%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20bilateral%20meetings%20is%20being%20finalised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20bilateral%20meeting%20takes%20place%2C%20it%20will%20be%20their%20first%20since%20the%20India-China%20border%20standoff%20began%20in%20May%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20and%20President%20Xi%20had%20a%20brief%20encounter%20at%20a%20dinner%20during%20the%20G20%20summit%20in%20Bali%20last%20November.%20China%20has%20already%20announced%20that%20Xi%20Jinping%20is%20travelling%20to%20South%20Africa%20to%20attend%20the%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20talks%20among%20local%20commanders%20of%20the%20Indian%20Army%20and%20Chinese%20PLA%20for%20confidence-building%20measures%20in%20eastern%20Ladakh's%20Depsang%20and%20Demchok%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20and%20Chinese%20troops%20are%20locked%20in%20an%20over%20three-year%20confrontation%20in%20certain%20friction%20points%20in%20eastern%20Ladakh%20even%20as%20the%20two%20sides%20completed%20disengagement%20at%20several%20places%20following%20extensive%20diplomatic%20and%20military%20talks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20China%20held%20the%2019th%20round%20of%20Corps%20Commander-level%20talks%20on%20August%2013%20and%20August%2014%20with%20focus%20on%20resolving%20pending%20issues%20at%20the%20standoff%20areas%20of%20Depsang%20and%20Demchok.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20joint%20statement%20called%20the%20talks%20%26quot%3Bpositive%2C%20constructive%20and%20in-depth%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20two%20sides%20have%20agreed%20to%20resolve%20the%20remaining%20issues%20in%20an%20expeditious%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDays%20after%20fresh%20round%20of%20high-level%20talks%2C%20the%20local%20commanders%20of%20the%20two%20militaries%20held%20a%20series%20of%20negotiations%20at%20two%20separate%20locations%20to%20resolve%20issues%20in%20Depsang%20Plains%20and%20Demchok.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Major%20General-level%20talks%20that%20began%20on%20Friday%20primarily%20focused%20on%20confidence-building%20measures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20talks%20between%20the%20local%20commanders%20were%20held%20over%20the%20next%20couple%20of%20days%20as%20well%20as%20on%20Monday%20to%20firm%20up%20confidence-building%20measures%2C%20according%20to%20people%20in%20the%20know%20of%20developments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20is%20no%20official%20word%20on%20the%20negotiations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2019th%20round%20of%20Corps%20Commander-level%20dialogue%20took%20place%20at%20the%20Chushul-Moldo%20border%20point%20on%20the%20Indian%20side%20of%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20(LAC)%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2024%2C%20National%20Security%20Advisor%20Ajit%20Doval%20met%20top%20Chinese%20Foreign%20Minister%20Wang%20Yi%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20a%20meeting%20of%20the%20BRICS%20nations%20in%20Johannesburg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20said%20Mr%20Doval%20conveyed%20that%20the%20situation%20along%20the%20LAC%20since%202020%20has%20%26quot%3Beroded%20strategic%20trust%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20public%20and%20political%20basis%20of%20the%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NSA%20emphasised%20the%20importance%20of%20continuing%20efforts%20to%20fully%20resolve%20the%20situation%20and%20restore%20peace%20and%20tranquility%20in%20the%20border%20areas%20so%20as%20to%20remove%20impediments%20to%20normalcy%20in%20bilateral%20ties%2C%20the%20ministry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExternal%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20also%20held%20talks%20with%20his%20Chinese%20counterpart%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20a%20meeting%20of%20the%20East%20Asia%20Summit%20in%20Jakarta%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20been%20maintaining%20that%20its%20ties%20with%20China%20cannot%20be%20normal%20unless%20there%20is%20peace%20in%20the%20border%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20eastern%20Ladakh%20border%20standoff%20erupted%20on%20May%205%2C%202020%2C%20following%20a%20violent%20clash%20in%20the%20Pangong%20Lake%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ties%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20nosedived%20following%20a%20fierce%20clash%20in%20the%20Galwan%20Valley%20in%20June%202020%20that%20marked%20the%20most%20serious%20military%20conflict%20between%20the%20two%20sides%20in%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%20of%20a%20series%20of%20military%20and%20diplomatic%20talks%2C%20the%20two%20sides%20completed%20the%20disengagement%20process%20in%202021%20on%20the%20north%20and%20south%20banks%20of%20the%20Pangong%20Lake%20and%20in%20the%20Gogra%20area.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692641880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fv3kbuuf8_pm-modi-xi-jinping-bali-ani_625x300_27_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpm-modi-jinping-xi-meeting-in-johannesburg-brics-summit-4316565%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20bilateral%20meetings%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20BRICS%20summit%20in%20Johannesburg%20are%20being%20fi