%20worded%20statement%20said%20the%20creation%20of%20the%20two%20districts%20%26quot%3Bremains%20alive%20as%20an%20unfinished%20issue%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20so%20it%20has%20become%20all%20the%20more%20%26quot%3Binevitable%20for%20the%20Nagas%20to%20register%20our%20opposition%20to%20the%20issues%20raised%20and%20incorporated%20in%20their%20memorandum%20submitted%20to%20different%20authorities%20as%20it%20is%20posing%20a%20big%20threat%20to%20the%20very%20existence%20and%20inalienable%20rights%20of%20the%20Nagas%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20state%20of%20Manipur%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20the%20UNC's%20statement%2C%20although%20not%20entirely%20unexpected%2C%20is%20significant%20as%20it%20brings%20the%20Nagas%20in%20the%20state%2C%20who%20have%20so%20far%20been%20speaking%20from%20the%20sides%20amid%20the%20Kuki-Meitei%20conflict%2C%20to%20the%20centre%20stage%20of%20the%20Manipur%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20ethnic%20violence%20broke%20out%20on%20May%203%20between%20the%20hill-majority%20Kuki%20tribes%20and%20the%20valley-majority%20Meiteis%20over%20the%20Meiteis'%20demand%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(ST)%20status%2C%20the%20Kukis%20have%20moved%20to%20demanding%20a%20complete%20separate%20administration%2C%20saying%20they%20can%20no%20longer%20co-exist%20with%20the%20Meiteis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22ec1496o8%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Fec1496o8_manipur-violence_625x300_28_May_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20separate%20administration%20demand%20initially%20came%20from%2010%20tribal%20MLAs%20in%20Manipur's%2060-member%20assembly%2C%20following%20nine%20days%20of%20major%20clashes%20in%20the%20India-Myanmar%20border%20trading%20town%20Moreh%2C%20Churachandpur%2C%20Imphal%20valley%20and%20other%20areas.%20The%20entire%20Kuki-Zo%20tribes%20eventually%20joined%20the%20MLAs%20in%20pushing%20for%20the%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20two%20districts%20created%20in%202016%2C%20the%20UNC%20said%20it%20was%20the%20%26quot%3Bhandiwork%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20then%20Congress%20government%20that%20allegedly%20took%20the%20decision%20for%20political%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOf%20the%20districts%2C%20the%20ones%20carved%20out%20from%20Senapati%20and%20Chandel%20districts%20are%20the%20handiwork%20of%20the%20Congress%20government's%20appeasement%20policy%20carried%20out%20in%20the%20name%20of%20administrative%20convenience.%20Hence%2C%20the%20demand%20of%20a%20separate%20administration%20which%20incorporates%20the%20so-called%20two%20new%20districts%20is%20necessarily%20opposed%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20UNC%20said%20in%20the%20statement%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Nagas'%20stand%20on%20the%20opposition%20remains%20unchanged.%20The%20bifurcation%20of%20the%20so-called%20two%20districts%20is%20an%20issue%20virtually%20with%20the%20Kukis%20only%2C%20not%20with%20the%20Zo%20peoples.%20In%20this%20regard%2C%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20people's%20representation%20to%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20European%20Parliament%2C%20UN%2C%20etc%20is%20on%20false%20territorial%20foundation%20and%20an%20attempt%20to%20befool%20those%20authorities...%26quot%3B%20the%20top%20Naga%20organisation%20that%20represents%20all%20Nagas%20in%20Manipur%20said%20in%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20180%20have%20died%20in%20the%20ethnic%20violence%20and%20thousands%20have%20been%20internally%20displaced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20security%20forces%20have%20created%20what%20they%20call%20%26quot%3Bbuffer%20zones%26quot%3B%20in%20areas%20between%20Meitei%20villages%20and%20Kuki%20settlements%20to%20avoid%20the%20two%20sides%20from%20fighting%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692639360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F5gl7kf2g_manipur-generic-debanish-credit_625x300_21_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2