%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20loves%20to%20learn%2C%20when%20treats%20are%20involved%20he%20puts%20his%20whole%20heart%20into%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Seifried%20said.%20%26quot%3BHe%20will%20spin%20around%20with%20excitement%20and%20try%20to%20offer%20all%20of%20the%20things%20he%20knows!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BKit%20Kat%20LOVES%20performing%20his%20tricks!%20He%20has%20been%20performing%20since%20he%20was%20a%20tiny%20kitten%20and%20you%20can%20tell%20how%20excited%20he%20is%20to%20get%20out%20on%20the%20floor%20to%20show%20off%20his%20stuff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692637320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F5q4ovq5g_kit-kat_625x300_21_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fwatch-cat-sets-guinness-world-record-with-jump-roping-feat-4317292%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kit%20Kat%20set%20the%20record%20for%20most%20skips%20by%20a%20cat%20in%20one%20minute%20with%20the%20help%20of%20its%20owner%20Trisha%20Seifried.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fwatch-cat-sets-guinness-world-record-with-jump-roping-feat-4317292%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fwatch-cat-sets-guinness-world-record-with-jump-roping-feat-4317292%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fwatch-cat-sets-guinness-world-record-with-jump-roping-feat-4317292%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWill%20Postpone%20Chandrayaan-3%20Landing%20To%20August%2027%20If%20...%26quot%3B%3A%20ISRO%20Scientist%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIf%20any%20factor%20regarding%20the%20lander%20module%20appears%20unfavourable%2C%20then%20the%20landing%20will%20be%20shifted%20to%20August%2027%2C%20said%20the%20Space%20Applications%20Centre-ISRO%20about%20Chandrayaan-3%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENilesh%20M%20Desai%2C%20director%20of%20Space%20Applications%20Centre-ISRO%2C%20Ahmedabad%20said%20that%20the%20decision%20regarding%20the%20landing%20will%20be%20taken%20based%20on%20the%20health%20of%20the%20lander%20module%20and%20the%20conditions%20on%20the%20Moon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20August%2023%2C%20two%20hours%20before%20Chandrayaan-3%20lands%20on%20the%20Moon%2C%20we%20will%20decide%20on%20whether%20or%20not%20it%20will%20be%20appropriate%20to%20land%20it%20at%20that%20time%20based%20on%20the%20health%20of%20the%20lander%20module%20and%20the%20conditions%20on%20the%20Moon.%20In%20case%2C%20if%20any%20factor%20appears%20to%20be%20not%20favourable%2C%20then%20we%20will%20land%20the%20module%20on%20the%20Moon%20on%20August%2027.%20No%20problem%20should%20occur%20and%20we%20will%20be%20able%20to%20land%20the%20module%20on%20August%2023%2C%E2%80%9D%20Director%20Desai%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EISRO%20Chairman%20and%20Secretary%20Department%20of%20Space%20S%20Somanath%20called%20on%20the%20Union%20Minister%20of%20State%20(Independent%20Charge)%20Science%20and%20Technology%2C%20Atomic%20Energy%20and%20Space%20Jitendra%20Singh%20in%20New%20Delhi%20today%20and%20apprised%20him%20of%20the%20status%20and%20readiness%20of%20%E2%80%98Chandrayaan-3'%20for%20the%20moon%20landing%20scheduled%20on%20August%2023%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChairman%20ISRO%20briefed%20the%20minister%20on%20the%20health%20status%20of%20Chandrayaan-3%20and%20said%20that%20all%20systems%20are%20working%20perfectly%20and%20no%20contingencies%20are%20anticipated%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20next%20two%20days%2C%20the%20health%20of%20Chandrayaan-3%20will%20be%20continuously%20monitored.%20The%20final%20sequence%20of%20landing%20will%20be%20loaded%20two%20days%20ahead%20and%20tested%20out%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20meeting%2C%20Minister%20Jitendra%20Singh%20expressed%20his%20confidence%20in%20%E2%80%98Chandrayaan-3'%20making%20a%20soft%20landing%20this%20time%20and%20hoped%20that%20it%20will%20script%20a%20new%20history%20of%20planetary%20exploration%20under%20the%20guidance%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EISRO%20said%20the%20Chandrayaan-3%20is%20set%20to%20land%20on%20the%20moon%20on%20August%2023%2C%202023%2C%20around%2018%3A04%20hours%20IST.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELive%20actions%20will%20be%20available%20on%20the%20ISRO%20website%2C%20its%20YouTube%20channel%2C%20Facebook%2C%20and%20public%20broadcaster%20DD%20National%20TV%20from%2017%3A27%20IST%20on%20Aug%2023%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Chandrayaan-2%20mission%20was%20only%20%E2%80%9Cpartially%20successful%E2%80%9D%20since%20the%20lander%20lost%20contact%20after%20a%20hard%20landing%2C%20the%20ISRO%20successfully%20established%20two-way%20communication%20between%20the%20Chandrayaan-3%20lander%20module%20and%20the%20still-orbiting%20Chandrayaan-2%20orbiter.%20In%20a%20significant%20development%2C%20the%20Chandrayaan-2%20orbiter%20which%20was%20already%20fixed%20around%20the%20moon%20established%20a%20two-way%20connection%20with%20the%20lander%20module%20of%20Chandrayaan-3%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20the%20ISRO%20shared%20new%20images%20of%20the%20lunar%20far%20side%20area%20captured%20by%20the%20Chandrayaan-3.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20will%20be%20the%20fourth%20country%20in%20the%20world%20to%20achieve%20this%20feat%20after%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Russia%2C%20and%20China%2C%20but%20India%20will%20be%20the%20only%20country%20in%20the%20world%20to%20land%20on%20the%20lunar%20south%20pole.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20primary%20objectives%20of%20the%20Chandrayaan-3%20mission%20are%20threefold%20--%20to%20demonstrate%20safe%20and%20soft%20landing%20on%20lunar%20surface%3B%20to%20demonstrate%20rover%20roving%20on%20the%20moon%2C%20and%20to%20conduct%20in-situ%20scientific%20experiments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrayaan-3's%20development%20phase%20commenced%20in%20January%202020%20with%20the%20launch%20planned%20sometime%20in%202021.%20However%2C%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic%20brought%20an%20unforeseen%20delay%20to%20the%20mission's%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJitendra%20Singh%20recalled%20that%20the%20first%20in%20the%20series%20of%20Chandrayaan%20--%20namely%20Chandrayaan-1%2C%20is%20credited%20for%20having%20discovered%20the%20presence%20of%20water%20on%20the%20surface%20of%20the%20Moon%2C%20which%20was%20a%20new%20revelation%20for%20the%20world%20and%20even%20the%20premier%20Space%20agencies%20like%20the%20USA's%20NASA%20(National%20Aeronautics%20and%20Space%20Administration)%20were%20fascinated%20by%20this%20discovery%20and%20used%20the%20inputs%20for%20their%20further%20experiments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrayaan-3%20mission%20was%20launched%20on%20July%2014%2C%202023%2C%20via%20the%20GSLV%20Mark%203%20(LVM%203)%20heavy-lift%20launch%20vehicle%20from%20the%20Satish%20Dhawan%20Space%20Centre%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh's%20Sriharikota%20at%202%3A35%20PM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20much-awaited%20soft%20landing%20of%20Chandrayaan-3%20on%20the%20south%20pole%20of%20the%20Moon%2C%20former%20director%20of%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%20and%20in-charge%20of%20the%20previous%20lunar%20mission%20%E2%80%98Chandrayaan-2'%2C%20K%20Sivan%20earlier%20today%20said%20that%20the%20mission%20will%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bgrand%20success%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt's%20a%20very%20anxious%20moment%E2%80%A6I'm%20sure%20that%20this%20time%20it%20will%20be%20a%20grand%20success%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Sivan%20said%20while%20speaking%20to%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20our%20own%20system%20and%20we%20will%20be%20establishing%20a%20soft%20landing%20without%20any%20problem.%20But%20it%20is%20a%20complex%20process%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20while%20responding%20to%20a%20question%20asked%20whether%20there%20would%20be%20any%20impact%20after%20the%20failure%20of%20Russia's%20Luna-25%20mission.%20Russia's%20moon%20mission%20failed%20after%20its%20Luna-25%20spacecraft%20spun%20out%20of%20control%20and%20smashed%20into%20the%20moon%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20corrective%20measures%20have%20been%20taken%20after%20going%20through%20data%20generated%20by%20the%20Chandrayaan-2%20mission.%20When%20asked%20if%20those%20additional%20systems%20too%20were%20indigenous%2C%20Sivan%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CEverything%20is%20indigenous.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20ISRO%20released%20images%20of%20the%20lunar%20far%20side%20area%20captured%20by%20the%20Lander%20Hazard%20Detection%20and%20Avoidance%20Camera%20(LHDAC).%20This%20camera%20assists%20in%20locating%20a%20safe%20landing%20area%20--%20without%20boulders%20or%20deep%20trenches%20--%20during%20the%20descent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20'Vikram'%20lander%20module%20of%20the%20spacecraft%20successfully%20separated%20from%20the%20propulsion%20module%20recently%2C%20and%20subsequently%20underwent%20crucial%20deboosting%20manoeuvres%20and%20descended%20to%20a%20slightly%20lower%20orbit.%20The%20Chandrayaan-3%20mission's%20lander%20is%20named%20after%20Vikram%20Sarabhai%20(1919%E2%80%931971)%2C%20who%20is%20widely%20regarded%20as%20the%20father%20of%20the%20Indian%20space%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20GSLV%20Mark%203%20(LVM%203)%20heavy-lift%20launch%20vehicle%20was%20used%20for%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20spacecraft%20that%20was%20placed%20in%20the%20lunar%20orbit%20on%20August%205%20and%20since%20then%20it%20has%20been%20through%20a%20series%20of%20orbital%20manoeuvres%20been%20lowered%20closer%20to%20the%20moon's%20surface.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20a%20month%20and%20seven%20days%20since%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20launched%20the%20Chandrayaan-3%20mission%20on%20July%2014.%20The%20spacecraft%20was%20launched%20from%20the%20Satish%20Dhawan%20Space%20Centre%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh's%20Sriharikota.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stated%20objectives%20of%20Chandrayaan-3%2C%20India's%20third%20lunar%20mission%2C%20are%20safe%20and%20soft%20landing%2C%20rover%20roving%20on%20the%20moon's%20surface%2C%20and%20in-situ%20scientific%20experiments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20approved%20cost%20of%20Chandrayaan-3%20is%20Rs%20250%20crores%20(excluding%20launch%20vehicle%20cost).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrayaan-3's%20development%20phase%20commenced%20in%20January%202020%20with%20the%20launch%20planned%20sometime%20in%202021.%20However%2C%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic%20brought%20an%20unforeseen%20delay%20to%20the%20mission's%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20scientific%20outcomes%20from%20Chandrayaan-2%20include%20the%20first-ever%20global%20map%20for%20lunar%20sodium%2C%20enhancing%20knowledge%20on%20crater%20size%20distribution%2C%20unambiguous%20detection%20of%20lunar%20surface%20water%20ice%20with%20IIRS%20instrument%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692636840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F5rjpr42o_chandrayaan3-image-of-moon_625x300_21_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-isro-scientist-will-postpone-chandrayaan-3-landing-to-august-27-if-factors-unfavourable-4316814%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20any%20factor%20regarding%20the%20lander%20module%20appears%20unfavourable%2C%20then%20the%20landing%20will%20be%20shifted%20to%20August%2027%2C%20said%20the%20Space%20Applications%20Centre-ISRO%20about%20Chandrayaan-3%20on%20Monday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-isro-scientist-will-postpone-chandrayaan-3-landing-to-august-27-if-factors-unfavourable-4316814%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%