0in%20Ottawa%20on%20Sunday%2C%20August%2020%2C%20to%20shed%20light%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9Curgency%20of%20addressing%20human%20rights%20violations%20in%20India%20and%20combating%20the%20rise%20of%20Hindutva%20(Hindu%20supremacist)%20extremist%20ideologies%20in%20Canada%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProtestors%20proceeded%20to%20Parliament%20Hill%20and%20then%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Office%20to%20symbolically%20deliver%20a%20joint%20letter%20with%20over%2080%20organisational%20signatories%2C%20including%20the%20South%20Asian%20Diaspora%20Action%20Collective%2C%20South%20Asian%20Network%20for%20Secularism%20and%20Democracy%2C%20Alternatives%20International%2C%20Canadian%20Council%20of%20Indian%20Muslims%2C%20Hindus%20for%20Human%20Rights%E2%80%94Canada%2C%20Indian%20Civil%20Watch%20International%2C%20International%20Council%20of%20Indian%20Muslims%2C%20Justice%20for%20All%20Canada%2C%20SADAN%20%E2%80%93%20South%20Asian%20Dalit%20Adivasi%20Network-%20Canada%2C%20among%20others.%20The%20protest%20was%20organised%20by%20an%20alliance%20of%2020%20diaspora%20organisations%20and%20diverse%20community%20partners%20from%20across%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20protest%20demonstrated%20that%20the%20concerns%20for%20minority%20rights%20and%20equality%20extend%20beyond%20borders%2C%20serving%20as%20a%20reminder%20that%20collective%20action%20remains%20essential%20in%20safeguarding%20these%20values%2C%20said%20a%20press%20release%20issued%20by%20organisers.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692636704000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F21221553%2FF4BLaVaWUAA3BJN.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fcanadian-groups-appeal-to-pm-trudeau-to-raise-voice-against-human-rights-violations-in-india%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Over%20a%20hundred%20protestors%20from%20several%20cities%2C%20including%20Montreal%2C%20the%20Greater%20Toronto%20Area%2C%20and%20Ottawa%20converged%20in%20Ottawa%20on%2