ctions%20resulting%20in%20a%20cleaner%2C%20greener%20and%20bluer%20future%E2%80%9D%20as%20a%20key%20goal%20of%20%E2%80%9CIndia%E2%80%99s%20G20%20presidency%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20explains%20this%20can%20only%20be%20achieved%20by%20%E2%80%9Cstriving%20for%20just%20and%20equitable%20growth%20for%20all%20in%20the%20world%2C%20as%20we%20navigate%20through%20these%20turbulent%20times%2C%20in%20a%20sustainable%2C%20holistic%2C%20responsible%2C%20and%20inclusive%20manner%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvoking%20the%20legacy%20of%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%8B%E2%80%8BMahatma%20Basaveshwara%2C%20Dayanand%20Saraswati%2C%20Ramakrishna%20Paramahamsa%2C%20Ishwar%20Chandra%20Vidyasagar%2C%20Mahatma%20Phule%2C%20Lokmanya%20Tilak%2C%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20and%20Dr%20Babasaheb%20Ambedkar%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcivil20.net%2Fc20-india-2023%2Fabout%2F%5C%22%3ECivil20%20(C20)%20India%20process%20was%20projected%20as%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9Cone%20of%20the%20official%20engagement%20groups%20of%20the%20G20%20that%20provides%20a%20platform%20for%20civil%20society%20organisations%20(CSO)%20around%20the%20world%20to%20voice%20people%E2%80%99s%20aspirations%20to%20the%20world%20leaders%20in%20G20.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20website%20states%20that%20it%20%E2%80%9Crepresents%20a%20democratic%2C%20participatory%2C%20and%20harmonious%20way%20of%20working%20together%E2%80%9D.%20C20%E2%80%99s%20goal%20is%20to%20%E2%80%9Cfocus%20on%20solving%20the%20socio-economic%20matters%20which%20touch%20the%20daily%20lives%20of%20the%20people%2C%20which%20include%20education%2C%20health%2C%20environment%2C%20technology%20and%20%3Cem%3Esewa%3C%2Fem%3E%20(sense%20of%20service)%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20C20%20process%20conducted%20under%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcivil20.net%2Fc20-india-2023%2Forganisation%2Fc20-india-chair%2F%5C%22%3Ethe%20guidance%20of%20spiritual%20leader%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcivil20.net%2Fc20-india-2023%2Forganisation%2Fc20-india-chair%2F%5C%22%3EMata%20Amritanandamayi%20(Amma)%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20has%20been%20curated%20to%20project%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcivil20.net%2Fvideos%2Fc20-inaugural-session%2F%5C%22%3Emajoritarian%20view%20of%20the%20country%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsing%20massive%20public%20resources%2C%20C20%20events%20involved%20only%20those%20civil%20society%20organisations%2C%20academics%20and%20media%20comfortable%20with%20the%20bigoted%20Hindutva%20vision%20of%20India%20that%20is%20ideologically%20core%20to%20the%20RSS%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20%E2%80%93%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20party.%20The%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20symbol%2C%20the%20lotus%2C%20is%20also%20etched%20into%20this%20year%E2%80%99s%20G20%20logo%2C%20leaving%20little%20doubt%20of%20its%20purpose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fg20-narendra-modi-one-india%5C%22%3EBefore%20%E2%80%98One%20World%2C%20One%20Family%2C%20One%20Future%E2%80%99%2C%20There%20Needs%20to%20Be%20%E2%80%98One%20India%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20became%20essential%2C%20therefore%2C%20for%20progressive%20and%20independent%20voluntary%20organisations%2C%20people%E2%80%99s%20movements%2C%20independent%20research%20initiatives%2C%20free%20academics%2C%20media%20etc.%20to%20articulate%20their%20concerns%20about%20how%20the%20G20%20process%20was%20being%20employed%20%E2%80%93%20to%20project%20a%20deliberately%20coloured%20version%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20polity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20important%20to%20highlight%20how%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20governing%20India%20and%20causing%20massive%20democratic%20deficits.%20Such%20voices%20would%20never%20find%20a%20place%20in%20the%20official%20G20%20or%20C20%20engagement%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20why%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwgonifis.net%2F2023%2F08%2F17%2Fdelhi-set-to-witness-we20-a-peoples-summit-on-g20%2F%5C%22%3EWe20%20Peoples%E2%80%99%20Summit%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20organised%20between%20August%2018%20and%2020%2C%202023%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwgonifis.net%5C%22%3EWorking%20Group%20on%20IFIs%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20HKS%20Surjeet%20Bhavan%20of%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20a%20space%20for%20the%20peoples%20of%20the%20G20%20countries%20%E2%80%93%20who%20collectively%20represent%20around%2085%25%20of%20the%20global%20GDP%2C%20over%2075%25%20of%20global%20trade%20and%20about%20two-thirds%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20population%20%E2%80%93%20to%20fathom%20risks%20in%20securing%20an%20inclusive%20and%20stable%20future%20in%20a%20fractured%20world%20riddled%20with%20crises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20Modi%20administration%2C%20We20%20offered%20an%20incredible%20opportunity%20to%20demonstrate%20to%20the%20world%20that%20it%20is%20serious%20about%20building%20an%20inclusive%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20when%20the%20We20%20proceedings%20were%20underway%2C%20a%20little%20before%20noon%20on%20August%2019%2C%20a%20massive%20battalion%20of%20the%20Delhi%20police%20swept%20in%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwe20-summit-g20-delhi-police-jairam-ramesh%5C%22%3Ecordoned%20off%20the%20area%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20military-style%20operation.%20Thus%2C%20the%20police%20effectively%20%3Cem%3Eimprisoned%3C%2Fem%3E%20over%20400%20delegates%20from%20across%20India%20who%20were%20inside%20Surjeet%20Bhavan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F19130257%2Fsignal-2023-08-19-130134_003-1024x461.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F19130257%2Fsignal-2023-08-19-130134_003-1024x461.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F19130257%2Fsignal-2023-08-19-130134_003-300x135.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F19130257%2Fsignal-2023-08-19-130134_003.jpeg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668688%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22378%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBarricades%20were%20placed%20by%20police%20at%20the%20New%20Delhi%20venue%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98We20%E2%80%99%20summit.%20Photo%3A%20By%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHundreds%20of%20participants%2C%20including%20elders%20and%20women%20from%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20communities%20who%20had%20travelled%20from%20very%20far%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20summit%20and%20ensure%20their%20voices%20were%20heard%20as%20well%2C%20were%20denied%20entry%20into%20the%20venue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParticipants%20were%20literally%20forced%20to%20stand%20by%20the%20cordoned%20gates%20and%20request%20the%20police%20to%20allow%20water%20and%20food%20to%20be%20passed%20through.%20Those%20outside%20were%20forced%20to%20stay%20on%20footpaths%20in%20the%20humid%20Delhi%20weather%20and%20under%20a%20scorching%20sun%2C%20without%20access%20to%20restrooms%20too.%20According%20to%20the%20police%2C%20the%20summit%20was%20being%20organised%20without%20their%20permission!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%20of%20the%20police%20action%2C%20the%20session%20that%20was%20underway%20was%20titled%3A%20%E2%80%98Does%20the%20Modi%20Administration%20Really%20Deliver%20on%20Tackling%20Climate%20Change%2C%20to%20Protect%20the%20Environment%2C%20Biodiversity%20and%20Associated%20Human%20Rights%2C%20as%20Claimed%20With%20G20%20and%20Other%20Global%20Fora%3F%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParticipating%20in%20this%20discussion%20were%20India%E2%80%99s%20former%20environment%20minister%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Jairam%20Ramesh%2C%20Medha%20Patkar%20of%20the%20Narmada%20Bachao%20Andolan%2C%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Anil%20Hegde%2C%20Vandana%20Shiva%20of%20Navdanya%20and%20the%20authors%20of%20this%20article.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20packed%20hall%20was%20engaged%20in%20deep%20conversations%20with%20the%20panel%20on%20how%20the%20Modi%20administration%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Finterview-why-there-is-mistrust-about-proposed-changes-to-forest-conservation-law%5C%22%3Eemasculated%20the%20Forest%20Conservation%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fbiological-diversity-amendment-bill-passed-in-rajya-sabha-by-voice-vote%5C%22%3EBiological%20Diversity%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20past%20few%20weeks%2C%20and%20that%20this%20fundamentally%20weakened%20global%20action%20to%20effectively%20tackle%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESomeone%20popped%20in%20to%20whisper%20the%20event%20was%20being%20forced%20shut%20by%20the%20police.%20Unfazed%2C%20the%20meeting%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJairam_Ramesh%2Fstatus%2F1692805395600023561%5C%22%3EJairam%20Ramesh%20tweeted%3C%2Fa%3E%20later%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20extraordinary%20that%20Delhi%20Police%20is%20stopping%20people%20from%20attending%20the%20We20%20meeting%20organised%20by%20activists%20representing%20We%2C%20The%20People%2C%20inside%20a%20building%20that%20belongs%20to%20the%20CPM.%20The%20meeting%20is%20perfectly%20peaceful.%20There%20are%20no%20street%20protests.%20I%20managed%20to%20enter%20at%2010%3A30%20am%20before%20Delhi%20Police%20started%20its%20operations%20but%20had%20difficulty%20exiting%20now.%20This%20is%20New%20India%20Democracy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F19173055%2FScreenshot-2023-08-19-at-5.28.39-1024x507.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F19173055%2FScreenshot-2023-08-19-at-5.28.39-1024x507.png%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F19173055%2FScreenshot-2023-08-19-at-5.28.39-300x149.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F19173055%2FScreenshot-2023-08-19-at-5.28.39.png%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668742%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22416%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPolice%20and%20security%20forces%20at%20the%20New%20Delhi%20venue%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98We20%E2%80%99%20summit.%20Photo%3A%20Debojit%20Dutta%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20matter-of-fact%20reference%20to%20%E2%80%9CNew%20India%20Democracy%E2%80%9D%2C%20a%20phrase%20Modi%20employs%20repeatedly%2C%20has%20frightening%20underpinnings.%20The%20Delhi%20police%20subsequently%20ensured%20that%20the%20We20%20Peoples%E2%80%99%20Summit%20did%20not%20proceed%20on%20Sunday%2C%20August%2020%2C%20with%20a%20letter%20issued%20by%20the%20Central%20District%20deputy%20commissioner%20of%20police%20(DCP)%20stating%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CRequest%20to%20hold%20meeting%20inside%20the%20premises%20and%20hall%20of%20HKS%20Surjeet%20Bhawan%20as%20part%20of%20G-20%20Summit%20by%20Working%20Group%20on%20IFIs%20on%2019%20%26amp%3B%2020.08.2023%20till%201800%20hours%20has%20been%20considered%20but%20due%20to%20law%20%26amp%3B%20order%2Ftraffic%20reason%2C%20and%20non-availability%20of%20the%20vital%20information%20pertaining%20to%20the%20gathering%2C%20visitors%2C%20etc.%20which%20is%20needed%20as%20per%20oreder%20%5Bsic%5D%20of%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20High%20Court%20of%20Delhi%20in%20W.P.(C)-2965%2F2023%2C%20dated%2010.03.2023%20above%20mentioned%20program%20is%20hereby%20rejected%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20review%20of%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%20citation%20reveals%20it%20was%20specific%20to%20one%20event%20held%20in%20March%202023%2C%20and%20has%20no%20cross-cutting%20implications%20whatsoever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20authors%20conducted%20a%20search%20of%20the%20Delhi%20police%20website%20with%20the%20keywords%20%E2%80%9Cpublic%20meeting%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Cprior%20permission%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CG20%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20reveals%20no%20orders%20or%20circulars%20have%20been%20issued%20over%20the%20past%20five%20years%20restricting%20the%20holding%20of%20such%20meetings%20or%20conventions%20or%20any%20other%20such%20events%20inside%20closed%20premises%2C%20anywhere%20in%20Delhi%20or%20in%20the%20sensitive%20central%20Delhi%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20review%20of%20the%20notifications%20issued%20(there%20are%20867%20records)%20reveals%20that%20on%20July%2012%20this%20year%2C%20the%20Central%20DCP%20issued%20one%20relating%20to%20ensuring%20public%20safety%20during%20the%20prevailing%20floods%20in%20Delhi%2C%20and%20another%20one%20on%20December%209%2C%202022%20inviting%20the%20public%20to%20reclaim%20recovered%20stolen%20articles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20written%20circular%20or%20order%20or%20notification%20issued%20by%20the%20Delhi%20police%20in%202022%20or%202023%20empowers%20the%20Central%20District%20DCP%20to%20declare%2C%20even%20if%20under%20duress%20%E2%80%93%20as%20is%20apparent%20from%20his%20letter%20%E2%80%93%20that%20the%20We20%20Peoples%E2%80%99%20Summit%20was%20being%20held%20illegally%20and%20can%20be%20shut%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20one%20were%20to%20examine%20the%20claim%20that%20the%20summit%20created%20law%20and%20order%20and%20traffic%20problems%2C%20anyone%20visiting%20the%20venue%20would%20notice%20that%20it%20was%20held%20in%20an%20orderly%20and%20absolutely%20peaceful%20manner%2C%20within%20Surjeet%20Bhavan.%20And%20barring%20a%20few%20parked%20rickshaws%2C%20taxis%20and%20cars%2C%20there%20was%20absolutely%20no%20traffic%20anywhere%20in%20a%20kilometre%E2%80%99s%20radius%20%E2%80%93%20and%20this%20was%20during%20the%20week%E2%80%99s%20working%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20why%20the%20Delhi%20police%20imagined%20it%20was%20essential%20for%20them%20to%20collect%20%E2%80%9Cvital%20information%20pertaining%20to%20the%20gathering%2C%20visitors%2C%20etc.%E2%80%9D%20begs%20the%20question%3A%20will%20they%2C%20on%20such%20a%20premise%2C%20shut%20down%20trains%2C%20metros%20and%20bus%20stations%2C%20hotels%2C%20marriage%20gatherings%2C%20corporate%20get-togethers%2C%20schools%2C%20colleges%2C%20hospitals%2C%20public%20offices%2C%20etc.%20because%20none%20of%20these%20institutions%20gathers%20such%20%E2%80%9Cvital%20information%E2%80%9D%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwe20-activists-blockade-police-modi-g20%5C%22%3EWe20%20Activists%20Brave%20the%20Blockade%20by%20Police%20Trained%20for%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20G-20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unfortunate%20police%20officer%E2%80%99s%20roving%20expedition%20in%20presenting%20rationality%20for%20what%20is%20clearly%20an%20attack%20on%20the%20fundamental%20rights%20of%20the%20citizens%20of%20this%20country%20to%20gather%20and%20conduct%20any%20event%20peacefully%20is%20how%20police%20power%20is%20being%20employed%20under%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20leaders%20of%20the%20G20%20gather%20in%20September%20in%20Delhi%2C%20they%20need%20to%20reflect%20on%20what%20they%20are%20doing%20to%20India%20and%20its%20liberal%20democratic%20traditions.%20They%20cannot%20shy%20away%20from%20taking%20responsibility%20for%20active%20efforts%20underway%20to%20quell%20open%2C%20free%20and%20critical%20discussions%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20G20.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20from%20Britain%2C%20the%20European%20Union%20and%20North%20American%20nations%20who%20espouse%20liberal%20democratic%20values%20need%20to%20take%20cognisance%20of%20this%20repressive%20state%20of%20affairs%20in%20India.%20It%20will%20not%20be%20an%20easy%20task%20when%20several%20of%20the%20G20%20leaders%20are%20noted%20as%20governing%20their%20countries%20in%20rather%20undemocratic%20and%20even%20ruthless%20ways%20by%20various%20independent%20global%20surveys.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20We20%20process%2C%20conducted%20independently%20without%20any%20fear%20or%20favour%2C%20introspected%20and%20interrogated%20vital%20concerns%20towards%20making%20the%20world%20a%20better%20place%20for%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20organised%20in%20the%20context%20of%20extensive%20climate%20change-related%20disasters%20across%20the%20world%20and%20brought%20to%20focus%20how%20existential%20crises%20due%20to%20climate%20change%20are%20colliding%20with%20the%20chaos%20resulting%20from%20neo-liberal%20economic%20models%2C%20manifesting%20in%20multiple%20ways%20in%20a%20multipolar%20world%20that%20is%20suffering%20from%20violent%20clashes%20between%20nations%20and%20amongst%20peoples%20within%20nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20summit%20delved%20deep%20into%20the%20six-agenda%20priorities%20for%20the%202023%20G20%20dialogue%2C%20such%20as%20green%20development%2C%20climate%20finance%20%26amp%3B%20LiFE%2C%20accelerated%2C%20inclusive%20and%20resilient%20growth%2C%20accelerating%20progress%20on%20sustainable%20development%20goals%2C%20technological%20transformation%20%26amp%3B%20digital%20public%20infrastructure%2C%20multilateral%20institutions%20for%20the%2021st%20century%2C%20and%20women-led%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20coming%20together%20of%20peoples%2C%20movements%2C%20trade%20unions%2C%20civil%20society%20organisations%2C%20concerned%20individuals%20and%20affected%20communities%20to%20deliberate%20on%20such%20critical%20issues%20should%20have%20been%20welcomed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20could%20have%20issued%20a%20direction%20to%20all%20his%20cabinet%20colleagues%20and%20ensured%20there%20were%20ministry%20representatives%20attending%20and%20listening%20to%20what%20people%20from%20across%20India%20%E2%80%93%20most%20of%20who%20had%20come%20with%20their%20own%20resources%20%E2%80%93%20were%20saying.%20Was%20the%20Modi%20administration%20so%20scared%20of%20learning%20the%20truth%20that%20it%20instead%20chose%20to%20shut%20down%20the%20We20%20Peoples%E2%80%99%20Summit%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELeo%20F.%20Saldanha%20and%20Bhargavi%20S.%20Rao%20are%20public%20policy%20analysts%20associated%20with%20Environment%20Support%20Group%2C%20an%20intersectional%2C%20intersectoral%20and%20interdisciplinary%20research%2C%20campaign%20and%20advocacy%20initiative%20based%20in%20Bangalore.%C2%A0%20They%20can%20be%20reached%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aleo%40esgindia.org%5C%22%3Eleo%40esgindia.org%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Abhargavi%40esgindia.org%5C%22%3Ebhargavi%40esgindia.org%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692626401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F21122023%2FIMG_3083.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwe20-summit-modi-truth-g20%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20the%20present%20administration%2C%20We20%20offered%20an%20incredible%20opportunity%20to%20demonstrate%20to%20the%20world%20that%20it%20is%20serious%20about%20building%20an%20inclusive%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A23%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwe20-summit-modi-truth-g20%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%20LG%E2%80%99s%20Approval%20to%20Use%20Gujarat%20Preventive%20Detention%20Law%20Raises%20Alarms%20on%20Unchecked%20State%20Power%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F01195459%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-06-01-at-4.40.30-PM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20deeply%20concerning%20and%20foreboding%20that%20the%20Delhi%20Lieutenant-Governor%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fexplained-law%2Fgujarat-pasa-act-lg-has-approved-for-delhi-8834910%2F%5C%22%3Eapproved%20the%20use%20of%20a%20Gujarat%20preventive%20detention%20law%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Delhi.%20This%20law%20grants%20the%20police%20the%20power%20to%20detain%20individuals%20for%20extended%20periods%20without%20trial%20and%20even%20before%20any%20actual%20offence%20is%20committed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20police%20have%20often%20displayed%20a%20blatant%20disregard%20for%20notions%20of%20fairness%2C%20impartiality%20and%20due%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20unabashedly%20pursued%20student%20activists%2C%20journalists%20and%20politicians%20opposed%20to%20the%20regime%2C%20creating%20an%20environment%20of%20fear%20and%20intimidation.%20This%20disturbing%20trend%20reached%20its%20peak%20with%20the%20police%E2%80%99s%20false%20implications%20of%20student%20activists%20under%20the%20draconian%20anti-terror%20law%2C%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20(UAPA)%2C%20and%20the%20law%20of%20sedition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20is%20afraid%20that%20giving%20the%20Delhi%20police%20powers%20under%20the%20draconian%20Gujarat%20Prevention%20of%20Anti-Social%20Activities%20Act%2C%201985%20will%20further%20fuel%20unaccountability%20and%20arbitrariness%20in%20their%20functioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreventive%20detention%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20coercive%20tools%20that%20a%20state%20in%20a%20constitutional%20democracy%20has%20at%20its%20disposal.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20the%20past%20has%20called%20it%20%E2%80%9Crepugnant%20to%20democratic%20ideas%20and%20an%20anathema%20to%20the%20rule%20of%20law%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Gujarat%20law%20is%20inherently%20arbitrary%20and%20sweeping%20in%20scope%2C%20enabling%20its%20massive%20and%20flagrant%20abuse.%20The%20high%20court%20of%20Gujarat%20has%20repeatedly%20censured%20the%20executive%20for%20misusing%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%20it%E2%80%99s%20shocking%20that%20the%20consent%20to%20extend%20the%20Gujarat%20law%20in%20Delhi%20was%20given%20without%20any%20public%20consultation.%20Though%20the%20subject%20of%20policing%20is%20outside%20the%20purview%20of%20the%20elected%20Delhi%20government%2C%20it%20does%20not%20mean%20that%20the%20elected%20government%20can%20be%20completely%20sidestepped%20on%20matters%20of%20law%20and%20order.%20On%20a%20matter%20as%20important%20as%20bringing%20into%20Delhi%20the%20preventive%20detention%20law%2C%20the%20LG%20should%20have%20consulted%20the%20chief%20minister.%20However%2C%20with%20an%20iron%20grip%2C%20the%20office%20of%20LG%20has%20arrogated%20despotic%20powers%2C%20effectively%20eclipsing%20the%20authority%20of%20the%20elected%20government%20in%20all%20important%20affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENewspapers%20have%20reported%20that%20the%20decision%20was%20taken%20after%20the%20Delhi%20police%20wrote%20to%20the%20L-G%20asking%20for%20a%20stricter%20law%20to%20deal%20with%20snatchers%20and%20drug%20peddlers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20a%20lame%20excuse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHas%20the%20crime%20of%20chain%20snatching%20and%20drug%20peddling%20in%20Delhi%20reached%20such%20proportions%20that%20it%20warrants%20action%20under%20preventive%20detention%20law%20instead%20of%20the%20normal%20process%20of%20investigation%20followed%20by%20a%20criminal%20trial%3F%20Why%20can%E2%80%99t%20snatchers%20and%20drug%20peddlers%20be%20booked%20under%20relevant%20provisions%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20and%20Narcotic%20Drugs%20and%20Psychotropic%20Substances%20Act%2C%201985%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20reliable%2C%20cogent%20data%20has%20been%20provided%20to%20justify%20the%20introduction%20of%20the%20Gujarat%20preventive%20detention%20law%20in%20Delhi.%20On%20the%20contrary%2C%20the%20introduction%20of%20such%20a%20harsh%20and%20unfair%20law%20to%20the%20national%20capital%20shows%20how%20the%20Delhi%20LG%20operates%20in%20an%20authoritarian%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreventive%20detention%20laws%20were%20justified%20in%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20debates%20as%20an%20evil%20necessity.%20Article%20246%20read%20with%20Seventh%20Schedule%2C%20List%20I%2C%20Entry%203%2C%20empowers%20the%20Parliament%20to%20pass%20preventive%20detention%20laws%20for%20reasons%20connected%20with%20defence%2C%20foreign%20affairs%20or%20security%20of%20India%2C%20and%20by%20List%20III%2C%20Entry%209%2C%20empowers%20the%20Parliament%20and%20state%20legislatures%20to%20pass%20these%20laws%20for%20reasons%20connected%20with%20the%20security%20of%20a%20State%2C%20the%20maintenance%20of%20public%20order%2C%20or%20the%20maintenance%20of%20supplies%20and%20services%20essential%20to%20the%20community.%20Article%2022%20provides%20important%20procedural%20safeguards%20against%20arbitrary%20and%20procedurally%20irregular%20preventive%20detention%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fgujarats-prevention-of-anti-social-activities-act-a-free-pass-for-arbitrary-detentions%5C%22%3EGujarat%E2%80%99s%20Preventive%20Detention%20Law%20Is%20a%20Free%20Pass%20For%20Police%20to%20Act%20Without%20Evidence%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOriginally%20intended%20for%20use%20in%20extraordinary%20situations%20threatening%20the%20security%20of%20the%20state%20or%20public%20order%2C%20the%20use%20of%20preventive%20detention%20laws%20has%20unfortunately%20become%20a%20routine%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20states%20like%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Telangana%20and%20Gujarat%20have%20enacted%20such%20laws%20as%20a%20convenient%20shortcut%20to%20bypass%20the%20normal%20process%20of%20laws%20and%20the%20rigours%20of%20the%20criminal%20justice%20system.%20The%20state%20laws%20are%20in%20addition%20to%20four%20central%20preventive%20detention%20laws%3A%C2%A0the%20Conservation%20of%20Foreign%20Exchange%20and%20Prevention%20of%20Smuggling%20Act%20(COFEPOSA)%2C%201972%3B%C2%A0the%20Prevention%20of%20Black%20Marketing%20and%20Maintenance%20of%20Supplies%20of%20Essential%20Commodities%20Act%2C%201980%3B%C2%A0the%20National%20Security%20Act%2C%201980%3B%C2%A0and%C2%A0the%20Prevention%20of%20Illicit%20Traffic%20in%20Narcotic%20Drugs%20and%20Psychotropic%20Substances%20Act%2C%201988.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%20to%20the%20existing%20central%20preventive%20detention%20laws%2C%20which%20focus%20on%20national%20and%20economic%20security%20matters%2C%20the%20state%20laws%20have%20transformed%20into%20catch-all%20measures%20that%20encompass%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20offences%20and%20situations%20unrelated%20to%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20security%20or%20public%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%202017%20onwards%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fcities%2FDelhi%2Fpreventive-detentions-in-2021-up-by-237-compared-to-year-before%2Farticle65853863.ece%23%3A~%3Atext%3DData%2520pertaining%2520to%25202021%2520showed%2Csix%2520months%2520of%2520their%2520detention.%5C%22%3Econsistent%20upward%20trend%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20number%20of%20individuals%20held%20in%20preventive%20custody.%20In%20the%20year%202021%20alone%2C%20the%20figure%20reached%20a%20staggering%201.1%20lakh%20people%2C%20showing%20an%20alarming%20surge%20of%20over%2023.7%25%20compared%20to%20the%20previous%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20majority%20of%20those%20detained%20were%20facing%20charges%20related%20to%20smuggling%2C%20bootlegging%2C%20theft%2C%20gambling%2C%20robbery%20and%20sexual%20offences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShockingly%2C%20the%20state%20of%20Gujarat%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fgujarats-prevention-of-anti-social-activities-act-a-free-pass-for-arbitrary-detentions%5C%22%3Ehas%20used%20the%20preventive%20detention%20law%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20detain%20individuals%20accused%20of%20GST%20evasion%2C%20unauthorised%20sale%20of%20anti-Covid%20medicines%2C%20cow%20smuggling%2C%20and%20even%20cases%20involving%20interfaith%20couples.%20This%20troubling%20data%20reveals%20an%20ever-widening%20net%20of%20preventive%20detention%20being%20cast%20for%20matters%20that%20extend%20far%20beyond%20the%20realm%20of%20national%20security%20or%20public%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreventive%20detention%20laws%20have%20become%20a%20convenient%20tool%20to%20bypass%20the%20rigorous%20procedures%20of%20criminal%20law.%20This%20includes%20evading%20the%20legal%20obligation%20to%20produce%20an%20accused%20before%20a%20magistrate%20within%2024%20hours%2C%20filing%20chargesheets%20within%2060%2F90%20days%2C%20presenting%20a%20compelling%20case%20for%20denial%20of%20bail%2C%20and%20ultimately%20proving%20guilt%20beyond%20reasonable%20doubt%20to%20secure%20a%20conviction.%20These%20crucial%20requirements%20of%20ordinary%20criminal%20law%20are%20willingly%20sacrificed%20in%20the%20name%20of%20maintaining%20public%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20state%20preventive%20detention%20laws%2C%20including%20the%20Gujarat%20law%2C%20are%20constitutionally%20suspect.%20They%20give%20arbitrary%20and%20unguided%20power%20to%20the%20executive%20without%20prescribing%20any%20guidelines%2C%20controls%20or%20checks%20for%20its%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20what%20point%20does%20the%20previous%20record%20of%20ordinary%20crimes%20transform%20an%20accused%20into%20a%20potential%20threat%20to%20public%20order%2C%20warranting%20their%20detention%20under%20preventive%20measures%3F%20Where%20does%20the%20threshold%20lie%20for%20offences%20such%20as%20video%20piracy%2C%20chain-snatching%2C%20bootlegging%2C%20or%20food%20adulteration%20to%20be%20perceived%20as%20jeopardising%20public%20order%3F%20Unfortunately%2C%20the%20statutes%20fail%20to%20offer%20any%20guidance%20on%20these%20vital%20aspects%2C%20leaving%20the%20matter%20shrouded%20in%20ambiguity%20and%20subject%20to%20arbitrary%20interpretation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20the%20Gujarat%20high%20court%20established%20a%20comprehensive%20set%20of%20guidelines%20that%20must%20be%20adhered%20to%20by%20authorities%20when%20issuing%20preventive%20detention%20orders.%20However%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20be%20clear%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20at%20best%20a%20mere%20band-aid%2C%20applied%20to%20a%20deeply%20disturbing%20crisis%20threatening%20the%20fundamentals%20of%20the%20rule%20of%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dangerous%20course%20of%20preventive%20detention%20laws%20is%20fuelling%20the%20descent%20into%20authoritarianism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20inadequate%20judicial%20scrutiny%20of%20state%20preventive%20detention%20laws.%20They%20have%20not%20been%20tested%20on%20the%20anvil%20of%20Articles%2014%2C%2019%20and%20Article%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20long%20ago%2C%20Justice%20Rohinton%20Nariman%20(now%20retired)%20presiding%20over%20a%20case%20of%20preventive%20detention%20under%20the%20Telangana%20statute%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fjudicial-intervention-barely-deters-telangana-ap-govts-from-abusing-preventive-detention-laws%5C%22%3Eexpressed%20astonishment%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20constitutional%20challenge%20to%20the%20validity%20of%20the%20State%20law%20in%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20preventive%20detention%20laws%20like%20the%20Gujarat%20Anti-Social%20Activities%20Act%20have%20effectively%20become%20a%20backdoor%20through%20which%20the%20state%20executive%20can%20thwart%20bail%20orders%20obtained%20by%20the%20accused%20or%20keep%20individuals%20imprisoned%20without%20securing%20a%20conviction%20through%20a%20fair%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incarceration%20of%20nearly%20one%20lakh%20people%20every%20year%20under%20a%20panoply%20of%20different%20preventive%20detention%20laws%20is%20a%20grim%20reminder%20of%20the%20serious%20curtailment%20of%20constitutionally%20guaranteed%20freedoms%20and%20civil%20liberties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EData%20also%20reveals%20that%20the%20majority%20of%20those%20detained%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Telangana%20under%20preventive%20detention%20laws%20hail%20from%20the%20poorest%20and%20most%20vulnerable%20sections%20of%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20police%20have%20repeatedly%20and%20shockingly%20demonstrated%20a%20flagrant%20disregard%20for%20the%20fundamental%20principles%20of%20fairness%2C%20and%20due%20process.%20The%20absolute%20worst%20scenario%20for%20Delhi%20is%20to%20further%20empower%20its%20police%20with%20additional%20arbitrary%20powers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAshish%20Khetan%20is%20an%20Associate%20Professor%20at%20Jindal%20Global%20Law%20School%2C%20Sonipat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692624652000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F01195459%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-06-01-at-4.40.30-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdelhi-lgs-approval-to-use-gujarat-preventive-detention-law-raises-alarms-on-unchecked-state-power%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Delhi%20police%20have%20often%20displayed%20a%20blatant%20disregard%20for%20notions%20of%20fairness%2C%20impartiality%20and%20due%20process.%20The%20absolute%20worst%20scenario%20for%20Delhi%20is%20to%20further%20empower%20its%20police%20with%20additional%20arbitrary%20powers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdelhi-lgs-approval-to-use-gujarat-preventive-detention-law-raises-alarms-on-unchecked-state-power%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Spain's%20FA%20chief%20says%20sorry%20after%20kissing%20player%20on%20the%20lips%20following%20their%20World%20Cup%20victory%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692624420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F08%2F768x432%2Fskynews-jenni-hermoso-luis-rubiales_6258133.jpg%3F20230821140919%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22http