kshik%20Mahasangh%20(ABRSM)%2C%20which%20has%20links%20to%20both%20the%20RSS%20and%20the%20BJP%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdditionally%2C%20Sau%20has%20also%20been%20an%20active%20member%20of%20the%20All%20Bengal%20University%20Teachers%E2%80%99%20Association%20(ABUTA)%20JU%20chapter%2C%20known%20for%20its%20connections%20to%20SUCI%20and%20WEBCUPA%20%E2%80%93%20the%20teachers%E2%80%99%20wing%20of%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tenure%20of%20JU%E2%80%99s%20last%20full-time%20vice-chancellor%20Suranjan%20Das%20ended%20on%20May%2031.%20Following%20that%2C%20the%20governor%20appointed%20Amitabha%20Datta%2C%20the%20pro-VC%20of%20the%20varsity%2C%20as%20the%20officiating%20vice-chancellor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20Sau%20led%20a%20delegation%20of%20teachers%20to%20the%20governor%20and%20made%20an%20official%20complaint%20against%20Datta%2C%20claiming%20that%20the%20latter%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3Erunning%20the%20campus%20through%20an%20ad-hoc%20mechanism.%20This%20led%20to%20Datta%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98s%20removal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20he%20was%20appointed%20as%20officiating%20VC%2C%20Sau%E2%80%99s%20past%20social%20media%20activity%20has%20attracted%20attention.%20On%20Facebook%2C%20he%20has%20shared%20a%20homophobic%20meme%2C%20while%20another%20presents%20a%20meme%20with%20questionable%20content%20regarding%20women.%20He%20has%20also%20expressed%20support%20for%20economic%20status%20as%20the%20criteria%20for%20reservations%2C%20not%20caste%2C%20aligning%20with%20the%20Sangh%E2%80%99s%20agenda.%20Sau%20has%20also%20shared%20a%20post%20endorsing%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F21184652%2Fsau-social-media.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F21184652%2Fsau-social-media.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F21184652%2Fsau-social-media-300x150.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F21184652%2Fsau-social-media-1024x512.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F21184652%2Fsau-social-media-800x400.jpg%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-669036%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EScreenshots%20of%20some%20posts%20that%20Buddadeb%20Sau%20has%20shared.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESau%E2%80%99s%20appointment%20has%20sparked%20widespread%20outrage%20and%20scepticism.%20Critics%20point%20to%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20ruling%20that%20stipulated%20that%20a%20VC%20must%20possess%20a%20minimum%20of%2010%20years%20of%20teaching%20experience%20as%20a%20professor%20in%20a%20university%2C%20which%20according%20to%20them%2C%20Sau%20falls%20short%20of.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20appointment%20raises%20questions%20about%20his%20eligibility.%20The%20ongoing%20power%20struggle%20between%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20and%20the%20governor%20over%20the%20VC%20position%20is%20further%20undermining%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20educational%20institutions%2C%E2%80%9D%20commented%20Sujan%20Chakraborty%2C%20a%20CPI(M)%20leader%20and%20an%20alumnus%20of%20the%20University.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENilasis%20Basu%2C%20a%20leader%20of%20CPI-ML%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Esaid%20that%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20governor%20has%20%E2%80%9Ccapitalised%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20turmoil%20in%20the%20university%20to%20%E2%80%9Cindirectly%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20the%20RSS%E2%80%99s%20involvement%E2%80%9D%20through%20the%20new%20VC.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20manoeuvring%20is%20part%20of%20a%20larger%20trend%20wherein%20individuals%20are%20strategically%20placed%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20educational%20institutions%20to%20undermine%20their%20integrity.%20This%20has%20been%20seen%20at%20institutions%20like%20Visva-Bharati.%20Now%2C%20the%20focus%20is%20on%20Jadavpur%20University.%20By%20complying%20with%20directives%20from%20the%20central%20government%2C%20the%20Governor%20has%20placed%20an%20individual%20with%20insufficient%20professorial%20experience%20as%20VC%2C%E2%80%9D%20Basu%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20BJP-RSS%20continues%20their%20efforts%20to%20infiltrate%20Jadavpur%20University%20in%20this%20manner%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20anticipated%20that%20resistance%20from%20the%20university%E2%80%99s%20students%20will%20grow%20stronger.%20Jadavpur%20University%20stands%20firm%20against%20the%20influence%20of%20the%20RSS%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20AISA%20leader%20remarked.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20governor%20has%20made%20Jadavpur%20University%20a%20lab%20for%20his%20experiments.%20We%20would%20get%20to%20know%20the%20result%20soon.%20Those%20who%20have%20been%20arrested%20%5Bin%20connection%20with%20the%20student%E2%80%99s%20death%5D%20are%20all%20left-wing%20activists.%20It%E2%80%99s%20clear%20who%20all%20were%20involved%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Trinankur%20Bhattacharya%2C%20state%20president%20of%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20Chhatra%20Parishad.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20recent%20times%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20making%20attempts%20to%20establish%20a%20foothold%20within%20the%20precincts%20of%20JU%2C%20where%20its%20sphere%20of%20influence%20has%20been%20limited.%20BJP%20leader%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%20last%20week%20visited%20Jadavpur%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fwest-bengal%2Fju-students-death-suvendu-adhikaris-jadavpur-university-visit-turns-chaotic-as-clashes-break-out%2Fcid%2F1959664%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20BJP%20after%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3Ehaving%20%E2%80%9Ctaught%20a%20lesson%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20so-called%20%E2%80%98Tukde-tukde%E2%80%99%20gang%20in%20JNU%2C%20will%20%E2%80%9Ccleanse%E2%80%9D%20Jadavpur%20as%20well%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20%E2%80%9Ctukde-tukde%20gang%E2%80%9D%20is%20a%20catch-all%20phrase%20that%20the%20BJP%20uses%20to%20refer%20to%20its%20critics.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESFI%20leader%20Mayukh%20Biswas%20said%20that%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EJadavpur%20University%20is%20among%20the%20best%20universities%20in%20the%20country%20but%20is%20still%20grappling%20with%20a%20severe%20financial%20crisis.%20%E2%80%9CInstead%20of%20providing%20assistance%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20and%20BJP%20are%20engaging%20in%20a%20struggle%20to%20deteriorate%20the%20university%E2%80%99s%20reputation.%20BJP%20is%20attempting%20to%20enter%20through%20the%20door%20left%20open%20by%20their%20representative%20to%20the%20Vice-Chancellor%E2%80%99s%20position.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20they%20created%20discord%20between%20the%20state%20government%20and%20the%20Governor%20in%20Kannur%2C%20Kerala%2C%20in%20a%20similar%20fashion.%20Our%20demand%20is%20for%20the%20punishment%20of%20the%20culprits%20%5Bin%20the%20student%E2%80%99s%20suicide%5D%2C%20and%20to%20protect%20the%20campus%2C%E2%80%9D%20Biswas%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECritics%20of%20Hindutva%20ideology%20fear%20that%20like%20it%20did%20with%20JNU%2C%20the%20BJP%20plans%20to%20gain%20a%20foothold%20in%20JU%20by%20appointing%20those%20sympathetic%20to%20its%20ideology%20in%20high%20positions.%20These%20critics%20say%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eby%20advocating%20for%20revisions%20that%20prioritise%20a%20specific%20historical%2C%20cultural%2C%20and%20religious%20perspective%2C%20the%20Hindutva%20movement%20aims%20to%20reshape%20the%20educational%20landscape%20in%20India%2C%20raising%20concerns%20about%20the%20role%20of%20academia%20in%20nurturing%20a%20free-thinking%2C%20diverse%2C%20inclusive%2C%20and%20tolerant%20citizenry.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWith%20inputs%20from%20Joydeep%20Sarkar.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692623935000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F07%2FJadavpur_Wikimediafeatures.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fjadavpur-university-new-vc-concerns-buddadeb-sau%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Due%20to%20Buddadeb%20Sau's%20association%20with%20unions%20that%20have%20links%20to%20the%20RSS-BJP%20and%20his%20past%20social%20media%20activity%2C%20concerns%20have%20been%20raised%20about%20the%20appointment.%20Others%20say%20he%20lacks%20the%20qualifications%20to%20satisfy%20the%20criteria%20laid%20out%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A67%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fjadavpur-university-new-vc-concerns-buddadeb-sau%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israeli%20woman%20shot%20dead%20in%20attack%20on%20car%20in%20southern%20West%20Bank%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692622356000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FECB3%2Fproduction%2F_130859506_mediaitem130859500.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-66570478%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20man%20was%20also%20injured%20when%20their%20car%20was%20targeted%20by%20gunfire%20on%20a%20highway%20south%20of%20Hebron.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A62%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-66570478%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-66570478.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-66570478.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22tit