0to%20journalists%2C%20Putellas%20far%20preferred%20to%20have%20her%20efforts%20on%20the%20pitch%20do%20her%20talking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20many%20felt%20the%20team%E2%80%99s%20chances%20leading%20into%20the%20World%20Cup%20hinged%20on%20their%20taliswoman%E2%80%99s%20return%20and%20skill%2C%20with%20fans%20believed%20Putellas%E2%80%99%20return%20to%20the%20team%20was%20far%20more%20important%20than%20the%20rest%20of%20the%2015%20players%20who%20were%20out%20in%20the%20cold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlexia%20and%20I%20have%20played%20together%20for%20so%20long%2C%E2%80%9D%20Hermoso%20told%20DW%20about%20her%20former%20Barcelona%20teammate.%20%E2%80%9CTo%20be%20living%20in%20this%20moment%20with%20one%20another%2C%20it%20is%20so%20special.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2029-year-old%20proved%20to%20only%20make%20a%20minimal%20impact%20and%20spending%20so%20little%20time%20on%20the%20field%20during%20the%20World%20Cup%20was%20a%20difficult%20pill%20to%20swallow%20for%20a%20player%20that%20is%20obsessively%20strict%20with%20her%20own%20exceptionally%20high%20standards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPutellas%20made%20no%20effort%20to%20hide%20her%20frustrations%20during%20the%20tournament%20from%20the%20sidelines%2C%20throwing%20a%20water%20bottle%20centimetres%20away%20from%20the%20bench%2C%20after%20being%20substituted%20in%20the%2046th%20minute%20against%20Zambia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20her%20injury%2C%20the%20dynamic%20midfielder%20played%20like%20the%20ball%20was%20glued%20to%20her%20boots%2C%C2%A0but%20the%20technically%20gifted%20individual%2C%20having%20had%20to%20re-learn%20how%20to%20walk%2C%20run%20and%20control%20the%20ball%2C%20spent%20most%20of%20the%20tournament%20struggling%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20the%20pace%20of%20the%20game%20and%20unable%20to%20provide%20the%20pinpoint%20accuracy%20so%20accustomed%20to%20her%2C%20to%20release%20Hermoso%20or%20Paralluelo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20the%20leader%20within%20her%20saw%20her%20constantly%20corral%20and%20encourage%20her%20team%2C%C2%A0something%20all%20the%20players%20craved%2C%20according%20to%20Hermoso.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20know%20how%20special%20Alexia%20is%2C%20how%20special%20she%20is%20for%20the%20team%20and%20how%20special%20this%20win%20is%20for%20her%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHermoso%E2%80%99s%20journey%20back%20to%20falling%20in%20love%20with%20football%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Hermoso%2C%20playing%20at%20the%20World%20Cup%20in%20Australia%20and%20New%20Zealand%20seemed%20impossible%20just%2012%20months%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%2C%20being%20Barcelona%E2%80%99s%20all-time%20leading%20goalscorer%2C%20having%20netted%20181%20times%20in%20224%20appearances%2C%20she%20found%20herself%20searching%20for%20a%20way%20out%20from%20the%20team%20she%20has%20supported%20since%20childhood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%202021-22%C2%A0season%2C%20following%20a%20tumultuous%20season%20off%20the%20pitch%20with%20the%20Barcelona%20fans%20directing%20much%20vitriol%20towards%20her%2C%20the%20forward%20moved%20to%20Mexican%20club%20Pachuca%20on%20a%20free%20transfer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20road%20to%20this%20point%20was%20really%20hard%2C%E2%80%9D%20Hermoso%20told%20%3Cem%3EDW%3C%2Fem%3E%20through%20tears.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20to%20go%20to%20Mexico%20just%20feel%20like%20a%20player%20again.%20To%20bring%20back%20my%20love%20and%20passion%20for%20football.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20many%20people%20in%20Spain%20were%20talking%20and%20still%20talk%20about%20me%2C%20who%20I%20am%2C%20how%20I%20play.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20demonstrated%20to%20those%20people%20that%20even%20though%20I%20am%2033%20years%20old%2C%20I%20am%20still%20capable%20of%20being%20a%20good%20player.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHead%20coach%20Vilda%20kept%20his%20faith%20in%20Hermoso%20to%20be%20adaptable%20between%20leading%20the%20line%20for%20La%20Roja%20and%20dropping%20into%20midfield%20to%20accommodate%20teenager%20Salma%20Paralluelo%2C%20who%20was%20named%20Young%20Player%20of%20the%20Tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJenni%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20responsibility%20on%20her%20shoulders%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vilda%20said.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20known%20Jenni%20for%20more%20than%2015%20years%2C%20she%20came%20here%20as%20the%20best%20version%20of%20her%2C%20she%20has%20given%20everything%20she%20can%20at%2033%20years%20of%20age%2C%20and%20I%20am%20so%20proud%20of%20her.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVilda%E2%80%99s%20decision%20paid%20off%20as%20Hermoso%2C%20who%20is%20also%20Spain%E2%80%99s%20all-time%20leading%20goalscorer%20with%2051%20goals%2C%20scored%20three%20times%20during%20the%20tournament%20and%20set%20up%20Paralluelo%E2%80%99s%20winning%20goal%20against%202019%20finalists%20Holland%20in%20their%20tightly%20fought%202-1%20extra-time%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLife%20is%20composed%20of%20moments%2C%E2%80%9D%20Hermoso%20reflected.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20moment%20where%20I%20had%20to%20leave%20the%20best%20team%20in%20the%20whole%20world.%20This%20moment%20now%2C%20it%20is%20the%20one%20I%20have%20been%20waiting%20for%2C%20for%20so%20long.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EParedes%E2%80%99%20authority%20offered%20welcome%20calmness%20at%20the%20back%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%2032%2C%20Paredes%20also%20knew%20to%20lift%20a%20trophy%20with%20Spain%20time%20was%20not%20in%20her%20favour%2C%20and%20she%20faced%20a%20difficult%20decision%20when%20the%20RFEF%20came%20out%20in%20support%20of%20Vilda%20as%20opposed%20to%20the%20players%20who%20had%20expressed%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20Barcelona%20captain%20not%20being%20one%20of%20those%20to%20send%20an%20email%2C%20her%20inclusion%20in%20the%20side%20was%20unclear%2C%20having%20made%20herself%20unavailable%20for%20selection%20until%20April%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Vilda%2C%20the%20experienced%20centre-back%E2%80%99s%20reintroduction%20into%20the%20team%20was%20one%20that%20required%20little%20thought.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20Paredes%E2%80%99s%20return%20after%20Spain%E2%80%99s%20friendly%20against%20China%20in%20April%2C%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EDW%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CShe%20is%20a%20great%20player%20and%20has%20been%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20of%20course%2C%20I%20am%20very%20happy%20to%20have%20her%20with%20us.%20We%20do%20not%20think%20about%20the%20past.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParedes%20was%20the%20only%20outfield%20player%20to%20play%20every%20minute%20of%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20and%20it%20was%20her%20calm%20head%2C%20decisiveness%20in%20the%20air%20and%20robustness%20against%20strikers%20that%20helped%20her%20marshal%20Spain%E2%80%99s%20back%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20dream%2C%E2%80%9D%20Paredes%20told%20%3Cem%3EDW%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20been%20very%20hard%20but%20we%20knew%20it%20was%20possible.%C2%A0These%20moments%20are%20historic%20for%20Spanish%20football.%20It%E2%80%99s%20difficult%20to%20put%20it%20into%20words%20but%20it%20means%20everything.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fworld-cup-spains-centurions-realize-long-held-dreams%2Fa-66581324%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20originally%20published%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%5C%22%3EDW%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flogs1279.xiti.com%2Fhit.xiti%3Fs%3D531599%26s2%3D2%26p%3Dthewire.in%3A%3AVolltexte%3A%3Athewire.in_Volltexte_JS%26di%3D%26an%3D%26ac%3D%26x1%3D1%26x2%3D2%26x5%3Dthewire.in_Volltexte_JS%26x6%3D1%26x8%3Den-VAS-Volltexte-JavaScript-thewire.in-dwde%26x10%3Dthewire.in%3A%3AVolltexte%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692615237000%2C%22visual%22%3A%