two%20cases%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20May%202%2C%20the%20high%20court%20had%20asked%20the%20CBI%20to%20probe%20the%20killing%20of%20Sengbath%20Marak%2C%20son%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Enokma%3C%2Fem%3E%20(chief)%20of%20Oragitok%20village%20in%20the%20West%20Garo%20Hills%20district%2C%20on%20May%204%2C%202015.%20As%20per%20the%20police%2C%20an%20encounter%20had%20taken%20place%20with%20militants%20from%20the%20banned%20Gano%20National%20Liberation%20Army%20(GNLA)%20at%20a%20lower%20primary%20school%20in%20the%20village%20where%20they%20allegedly%20took%20shelter.%20Though%20the%20police%20had%20asked%20them%20to%20surrender%2C%20they%20opened%20fire%20and%20the%20police%20retaliated.%20The%20police%20claimed%20that%2033-year-old%20Sengbath%20was%20among%20the%20militants.%20According%20to%20the%20police%20version%2C%20he%20came%20out%20of%20the%20house%20and%20was%20shot%20on%20his%20leg.%20Thereafter%2C%20he%20tried%20fleeing%20the%20spot%20and%20was%20killed%20by%20the%20police%20team.%20The%20police%20called%20him%20a%20militant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20villagers%20countered%20the%20police%20version%20of%20the%20killing%2C%20called%20it%20%E2%80%9Cstaged%E2%80%9D.%20Sengbath%E2%80%99s%20father%2C%20thereafter%2C%20petitioned%20the%20Meghalaya%20high%20court%2C%20saying%20it%20was%20a%20fake%20encounter%20and%20demanding%20a%20probe%20into%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheshillongtimes.com%2F2023%2F05%2F03%2Fhc-asks-cbi-to-investigate-oragitok-encounter-case%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EShillong%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20news%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20stated%20that%20as%20per%20the%20villagers%2C%20stones%20were%20thrown%20at%20Sengbath%E2%80%99s%20house%2C%20leading%20him%20to%20come%20out%20of%20the%20house.%20Immediately%2C%20he%20was%20shot%20on%20the%20leg%20and%20then%20when%20he%20tried%20to%20flee%2C%20he%20was%20shot%20multiple%20times%2C%20leading%20to%20his%20death.%20After%20hearing%20both%20sides%2C%20th