%5C%22wp-image-327709%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22698%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWoodway%20Heritage%20Home%20is%20situated%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20glorious%20Western%20Ghats%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Susmitha%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShreedev%20was%20working%20in%20Bengaluru%20in%202000%20when%20he%20met%20Susmitha%2C%20an%20MBA%20graduate.%20The%20two%20fell%20in%20love%2C%20got%20married%2C%20and%20moved%20back%20to%20Chikmagalur%2C%20in%20a%20home%207%20km%20from%20the%20Woodway%20estate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ravages%20of%20time%20were%20evident%20on%20Woodway.%20It%20had%20been%20locked%20for%20a%20year-and-a-half%20and%20the%20unpredictable%20climate%20of%20the%20state%20had%20taken%20its%20toll%20on%20the%20home.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20starting%20to%20crumble.%20The%20Mangalore%20tiles%20and%20mud%20walls%20were%20starting%20to%20chip%20away.%20When%20we%20saw%20it%20after%20all%20these%20years%2C%20we%20could%20tell%20it%20had%20seen%20much%20damage%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Susmitha.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20tough%20call%20awaited%20the%20couple.%20Should%20they%20restore%20the%20home%2C%20furnish%20it%20or%20leave%20it%20as%20is%3F%20But%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F284474%2Fhow-couple-quit-city-life-to-build-sustainable-homestay-in-uttarakhand%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esentimental%20value%20of%20the%20home%20%3C%2Fa%3Ecompelled%20them%20to%20choose%20the%20first%20option.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20we%E2%80%99re%20so%20glad%20we%20did%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20simple%20idea%20taking%20roots%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20couple%20decided%20to%20restore%20the%20place%2C%20they%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20thought%20of%20converting%20it%20into%20a%20homestay.%20The%20inspiration%20came%