ears%20in%20talks%20with%20the%20tourism%20board%20of%20the%20state.%20They%20also%20visited%20tourism%20fairs%20across%20India%20to%20learn%20firsthand%20how%20to%20set%20up%20a%20homestay%20and%20everything%20else%20it%20entailed.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPHOTO-2023-03-26-14-00-08-1692369147.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20furniture%20in%20the%20heritage%20home%20is%20from%20the%20original%20house%20to%20maintain%20the%20antique%20vibe%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPHOTO-2023-03-26-14-00-08-1692369147.jpg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPHOTO-2023-03-26-14-00-08-1692369147-300x231.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPHOTO-2023-03-26-14-00-08-1692369147-500x384.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPHOTO-2023-03-26-14-00-08-1692369147-768x590.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPHOTO-2023-03-26-14-00-08-1692369147-1536x1181.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPHOTO-2023-03-26-14-00-08-1692369147-150x115.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-327707%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221230%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20furniture%20in%20the%20heritage%20home%20is%20from%20the%20original%20house%20to%20maintain%20the%20antique%20vibe%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Susmitha%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20do%20it%20the%20right%20way%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shreedev.%20%E2%80%9CWhenever%20we%20spoke%20to%20people%20about%20what%20we%20were%20trying%20to%20do%2C%20we%20never%20marketed%20Woodway.%20We%20marketed%20Chikmagalur.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20paid%20off.%20He%20wanted%20city%20folks%20to%20experience%20the%20magic%20of%20nature%20and%20the%20healing%20powers%20of%20solitude.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20it%20takes%20to%20run%20the%20estate%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERubbishing%20the%20usual%20assumption%20that%20coffee%20planters%20lead%20luxurious%20lives%2C%20Shreedev%20says%20that%20it%20is%20not%20that%20simple%20or%20rosy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20our%20quality%20of%20life%20is%20very%20good%20but%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20that%20goes%20into%20it.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F90205%2F10-sustainable-homestays-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFarming%20on%20plantations%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20hard.%20Managing%20250%20acres%20of%20land%20is%20tough.%20And%20that%20is%20the%20side%20that%20few%20see%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20every%20night%20after%20a%20tedious%20and%20laborious%20day%20at%20the%20plantations%2C%20Shreedev%20returns%20home%20with%20freshly-harvested%20coffee%20beans%20%E2%80%94%20that%20the%20guests%20wait%20eagerly%20for%20%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20deep%20sense%20of%20satisfaction.%20The%20plantations%20are%20where%20he%20belongs%2C%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurrounded%20by%20the%20plantations%2C%20Woodway%2C%20with%20its%20six%20fully-furnished%20rooms%20replete%20with%20modern%20amenities%20that%20complement%20the%20old-world%20charm%2C%20also%20houses%20a%20kitchen%20garden.%20The%20couple%20started%20working%20on%20their%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F297379%2Fcouple-set-up-eco-friendly-homestay-in-nilgiris-jungle-hut-harvests-solar-power%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epassion%20project%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202000%2C%20fixing%20the%20roof%2C%20electrical%20lines%20and%20painting%2C%20while%20preserving%20the%20original%20look%20and%20feel%20of%20the%20home.%20Shreedev%20gives%20the%20credit%20of%20overseeing%20the%20restoration%20to%20Susmitha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201125px)%20100vw%2C%201125px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FIMG_1091_11zon-1692369236.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221125%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20kitchen%20garden%20at%20Woodway%20Heritage%20Bungalow%20boasts%20of%20a%20variety%20of%20produce%20and%20guests%20can%20also%20enjoy%20a%20barbeque%20on%20the%20land%20in%20the%20evenings%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FIMG_1091_11zon-1692369236.jpg%201125w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FIMG_1091_11zon-1692369236-300x186.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FIMG_1091_11zon-1692369236-500x310.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FIMG_1091_11zon-1692369236-768x477.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FIMG_1091_11zon-1692369236-150x93.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-327708%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22698%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20kitchen%20garden%20at%20Woodway%20Heritage%20Bungalow%20boasts%20of%20a%20variety%20of%20produce%20and%20guests%20can%20also%20enjoy%20a%20barbeque%20on%20the%20land%20in%20the%20evenings%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Susmitha%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20the%20furniture%20is%20from%20the%20original%20house%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20notes.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20use%20brass%20vessels%20that%20were%20used%20for%20cooking%20back%20in%20the%20day.%20Everything%20is%20designed%20around%20taking%20the%20guests%20back%20a%20100