e%20set%20has%20to%20become%20a%2010-minute%20one%20because%20I%E2%80%99m%20going%20to%20break%20everything%20down%20slowly%2C%20and%20therein%20the%20humour%20came%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20recent%20special%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20see%20Navin%20explaining%20top%20and%20bottom%20%5Bsex%20positions%5D%20to%20people.%20These%20jokes%20are%20the%20outcome%20of%20trialling%20them%20for%20years%20before%20implementing%20them%20in%20real%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20when%20I%20say%20jokes%20like%2C%20%E2%80%98Kerala%20is%20bottom%2C%20Delhi%20is%20top%E2%80%99%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20call%20back%20to%20the%20audience%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20also%20an%20inbuilt%20joke%20as%20well.%20The%20demographic%20of%20the%20country%20also%20is%20very%20vivid%20in%20terms%20of%20sexual%20preferences.%20The%20%E2%80%98top%20and%20bottom%E2%80%99%20joke%20has%20become%20a%20reel%20on%20my%20Instagram%20handle.%20If%20you%20read%20the%20comments%20section%20right%20now%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20full%20of%20gay%20people%20trying%20to%20hook%20up%20with%20each%20other.%20What%20I%20like%20about%20queer%20culture%20is%20that%20we%20somehow%20find%20a%20way%20to%20thrive%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Navin.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ETaking%20the%20straights%20to%20gay%20school.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EMy%20full%20special%20is%20here%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FH9W4FYuVnj%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FH9W4FYuVnj%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FMl5xm3p3OW%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FMl5xm3p3OW%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Navin%20Noronha%20(%40HouseOfNoronha)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHouseOfNoronha%2Fstatus%2F1673571572509208576%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%2027%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20finding%20new%20avenues%20to%20tell%20jokes%2C%20Navin%20has%20over%20the