0their%20photo%2C%20biodata%2C%20Instagram%20link%2C%20Spotify%20link%20and%20sometimes%20even%20a%20link%20to%20their%20HIV%20test%20results%20on%20their%20social%20media%20handles.%20I%20envy%20them.%20What%20I%20love%20is%20that%20they%20have%20access.%20Growing%20up%2C%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20YouTube%2C%20TikTok%20or%20Instagram%2C%20i.e.%20an%20outlet%20%5Bwhere%20we%20could%20express%20our%20queer%20identities%5D.%20For%20me%2C%20comedy%20was%20an%20outlet.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20of%20them%20are%20so%20fierce%20with%20makeup.%20I%20never%20had%20the%20courage%20to%20wear%20makeup%20in%20my%20younger%20days.%20Today%2C%20you%20have%20young%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F289628%2Fbengaluru-drag-artist-queen-beyonce-pride-month%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edrag%20queens%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20drag%20kings%20and%20gender%20benders%20putting%20themselves%20out%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHaving%20said%20that%2C%20there%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20who%20are%20still%20getting%20kicked%20out%20of%20their%20houses%20for%20being%20gay%20and%20they%E2%80%99re%20still%20facing%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20same%20issues%20we%20faced.%20But%20what%20the%20queer%20community%20has%20now%20is%20a%20more%20prominent%20public%20voice%20and%20a%20face%20with%20important%20changes%20in%20the%20law%20to%20protect%20us.%20Also%2C%20there%20are%20so%20many%20nonprofits%20working%20behind%20the%20scenes%20to%20assist%20queer%20people%20in%20times%20of%20trouble.%20My%20job%20is%20nothing%20in%20comparison%20to%20all%20the%20people%20on%20the%20ground%20like%20the%20lawyers%20and%20activists%20who%20are%20filing%20these%20appeals%20and%20public%20interest%20litigations%20(PILs)%20in%20these%20landmark%20cases%20for%20queer%20rights.%20My%20job%20has%20been%20more%20on%20the%20sidelines%20like%20a%20jester%20saying%20%E2%80%98hey%20lo