gn%20thinking%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20try%20to%20promote%20positive%20interaction%20among%20peers.%20It%20helps%20them%20to%20build%20critical%20awareness%20and%20negotiations%20among%20team%20members%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERennis%20and%20his%20team%20work%20with%20any%20school%20for%20about%20four%20years%2C%20but%20remain%20in%20contact%20with%20the%20school%20to%20trace%20the%20impact.%20For%20instance%2C%20his%20team%20worked%20in%20Banapuram%20village%20of%20Telangana%20in%202010.%20After%20five%20years%20of%20this%20intervention%2C%20he%20says%2C%2090%20percent%20of%20the%20children%20going%20to%20schools%20in%20the%20villages%20were%20enrolled%20in%20higher%20education%20in%20colleges.%20%E2%80%9CIn%202019%2C%20we%20did%20a%20study%20to%20check%20what%20happened%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years.%20We%20found%20that%20all%20the%20girls%20were%20still%20in%20school%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20teaching%20the%20students%20through%20interactive%20sessions%2C%20they%20work%20to%20create%20a%20pool%20of%20teachers%20who%20can%20think%20of%20innovative%20ways%20to%20teach%20children%20after%20they%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-1691584663.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rennis%20charges%20up%20to%20Rs%20700%20per%20student%20per%20year%20from%20low-cost%20private%20schools.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-1691584663.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-1691584663-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fignis-careers-1691584663-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2